'''斯嘉丽·英格麗·约翰逊'''（{{lang-en|Scarlett Ingrid Johansson}}，{{bd|1984年|11月22日}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/11/Scarlett-Johansson.html|title=Scarlett Johansson (1984- )|publisher=FilmReference.com|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025223937/http://www.filmreference.com/film/11/Scarlett-Johansson.html|archive-date=2014-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一名[[美國|美國]][[女演员|女演员]]和[[歌手|歌手]]。童星出身，她的银幕处女作是1994年电影《{{link-en|浪子保镖|North (1994 film)}}》，随后，她凭借在《{{link-en|曼妮姐妹|Manny & Lo}}》（1996）中的演出获得了美国[[獨立精神獎|獨立精神獎]]最佳女主角的提名，参演《[[轻声细语|轻声细语]]》（1998）和《[[黐孖妹|黐孖妹]]》（2001）又带给她更多好评和名气。2003年，她开始转型扮演成年角色，主演了《[[戴珍珠耳環的少女_(電影)|戴珍珠耳环的少女]]》和《[[迷失东京|迷失东京]]》两部影片，她因此赢得两个[[金球奖|金球奖]]提名，《迷失东京》也为她赢得了[[英國電影學院獎最佳女主角|英國電影學院獎最佳女主角]]。

《{{link-en|献给你的情歌|A Love Song for Bobby Long}}》（2004）和[[伍迪·艾伦|伍迪·艾伦]]《[[赛末点|赛末点]]》（2005）中的两个角色使约翰逊两次获得金球奖提名。她随后的作品包括《[[绝地再生|绝地再生]]》（2005）、《[[艷屍案中案|艷屍案中案]]》（2006）、《[[顶尖对决|顶尖对决]]》（2006）、《[[午夜巴塞罗那|午夜巴塞罗那]]》（2008）等。她在《[[超急情聖|超急情聖]]》（2013）和《[[皮囊之下|皮囊之下]]》（2014）中的表演亦获得很高评价。

自2010年起，约翰逊在[[漫威电影宇宙|漫威电影宇宙]]中扮演[[漫威漫畫|漫威漫畫]]角色人物[[黑寡婦_(復仇者聯盟)|黑寡妇]]<ref name="WinterSoldier">{{cite web |first=Mike |last=Fleming |title=Five Actresses Testing For 'Captain America 2′ Role; Black Widow Might Drop By As Well |publisher=Deadline.com |url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/10/five-actresses-testing-for-captain-america-2-role-black-widow-might-drop-by-as-well/ |date=2012-10-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6B7naLneH?url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/10/five-actresses-testing-for-captain-america-2-role-black-widow-might-drop-by-as-well/ |archivedate=2012-10-02 |accessdate=2017-06-08 }}</ref>。2019年，约翰逊憑著《[[婚姻故事|婚姻故事]]》的表演入圍金球獎、美國演員工會獎和英國電影學院獎，並首次獲奧斯卡獎提名，同時其在《[[兔嘲男孩|兔嘲男孩]]》的演繹也入選女配角獎，使她成為自2007年的[[凱特·布蘭琪|凱特·布蘭琪]]後，12年來首位在[[同年獲兩項奧斯卡金像獎提名演員列表|同屆奧斯卡中取得兩項演藝類別提名的演員]]。

2010年，[[百老汇|百老汇]]复排[[亚瑟·米勒|亚瑟·米勒]]的作品《{{link-en|桥头眺望|A View from the Bridge}}》，约翰逊参演其中，并获得[[托尼奖|托尼奖]]最佳舞台劇女配角。作为歌手的她有两张专辑作品，《{{lang|en|{{link-en|Anywhere I Lay My Head|Anywhere I Lay My Head}}}}》和《{{lang|en|{{link-en|Break Up|Break Up}}}}》。

约翰逊被认为是当代[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]的[[性感象征|性感象征]]，也进入过许多「世界性感女性」的列表，最有名的便是《[[时尚先生_(刊物)|时尚先生]]》杂志在2006和2013年两度将其列为「当今最性感女性」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.businessinsider.com/scarlett-johansson-esquires-sexiest-woman-alive-2013-2013-10 |title=Scarlett Johansson Esquire's Sexiest Woman Alive 2013 - Business Insider<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906005212/http://www.businessinsider.com/scarlett-johansson-esquires-sexiest-woman-alive-2013-2013-10 |archive-date=2014-09-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Sexiest Woman Alive">{{cite news|last=Jacob|first=AJ|title=Scarlett Johansson Is the Sexist Woman Alive|work=Esquire|date=2006-10-31|url=http://www.esquire.com/women/the-sexiest-woman-alive/scarlett-johansson-pics|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004443/http://www.esquire.com/women/the-sexiest-woman-alive/scarlett-johansson-pics|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57606279/scarlett-johansson-named-sexiest-woman-alive CBS News, "Scarlett Johansson named sexiest woman alive"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57606279/scarlett-johansson-named-sexiest-woman-alive |date=20140906004451 }} CBS/AP</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=斯嘉丽再度当选全球最性感女性|url=http://www.yoka.com/beauty/starface/2013/pic1010831097.shtml|accessdate=2014-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714114605/http://www.yoka.com/beauty/starface/2013/pic1010831097.shtml|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，使她成为唯一一位两次夺此殊荣的女性。2007年，《[[花花公子|花花公子]]》杂志也将其列为「最性感名人」<ref name="Sexiest Celebrity">{{cite news|title=Playboy Names Scarlett Johansson|publisher=PopCrunch Celebrity Gossip Blog|date=2007-02-19|url=http://www.popcrunch.com/playboy-names-scarlett-johansson-2007s-sexiest-celebrity|accessdate=2014-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815015359/http://www.popcrunch.com/playboy-names-scarlett-johansson-2007s-sexiest-celebrity|archive-date=2014-08-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==早年生活==

史嘉蕾·喬韓森於 [[1984年|1984年]] 11 月 22 日出生於紐約市[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]區。<ref>{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson|url=https://www.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2bb3f264dd|access-date=November 20, 2018|publisher=[[British_Film_Institute|British Film Institute]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181117133615/http://www.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2bb3f264dd|archive-date=November 17, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson: 'La monogamia es antinatural'|url=http://www.eitb.eus/es/television/programas/la-noche-de/detalle/4731594/curiosidades-secretos-vida-actriz-scarlett-johansson/|access-date=October 6, 2017|date=March 28, 2017|publisher=[[EITB|EITB]]|language=es-ES|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006211645/http://www.eitb.eus/es/television/programas/la-noche-de/detalle/4731594/curiosidades-secretos-vida-actriz-scarlett-johansson/|archive-date=October 6, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="PBS">{{cite web|title=Season 4 Official Trailer|url=https://www.pbs.org/video/finding-your-roots-season-four-official-trailer-hdf5ii/|access-date=September 8, 2017|work=[[Finding_Your_Roots|Finding Your Roots]]|publisher=[[PBS|PBS]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908111325/http://www.pbs.org/video/finding-your-roots-season-four-official-trailer-hdf5ii/|archive-date=September 8, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref> 她的父親 Karsten Olaf Johansson 是一位出身丹麥[[哥本哈根|哥本哈根]]的建築師。她的祖父 Ejner Johansson 是一位[[藝術史|藝術史]]學者、[[編劇|編劇]]和[[電影導演|電影導演]]，她的曾祖父則屬於[[瑞典人|瑞典人]]。<ref name="tirti2">{{cite news|url=https://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/theticket/2012/0427/1224315215457.html|newspaper=[[The_Irish_Times|The Irish Times]]|date=April 27, 2012|title='I'm not anything like her...'|access-date=April 16, 2013|archive-date=April 27, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427065747/http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/theticket/2012/0427/1224315215457.html}}</ref><ref name="fdr1">Stated on ''[[Finding_Your_Roots|Finding Your Roots]]'', [[PBS|PBS]], October 31, 2017.</ref> 她的母親梅蘭妮·斯隆（Melanie Sloan）出身紐約，曾任[[電影製片人|電影製片人]]；她的祖先是居住於波蘭及俄羅斯的[[德系猶太人|德系猶太人]]，原先姓氏為 Schlamberg<ref name="fdr12">Stated on ''[[Finding_Your_Roots|Finding Your Roots]]'', [[PBS|PBS]], October 31, 2017.</ref>，喬韓森也因此稱自己是猶太人。<ref name="femau1">{{cite news|last=Fischer|first=Paul|title=Scarlett Johansson The Spirit Interview|url=https://www.female.com.au/scarlett-johansson-the-spirit-interview.htm|publisher=Female.com|date=2008|access-date=September 19, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507225417/https://www.female.com.au/scarlett-johansson-the-spirit-interview.htm|archive-date=May 7, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="ashref2">{{cite news|title=Scarlett Johansson's a Jew, too|url=https://www.jta.org/2008/03/23/news-opinion/scarlett-johanssons-a-jew-too|publisher=[[Jewish_Telegraphic_Agency|Jewish Telegraphic Agency]]|date=March 23, 2008|access-date=March 23, 2008|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120101172646/http://www.jta.org/news/article/2008/03/23/107668/johanssonportman|archive-date=January 1, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson: from starlet to sci-fi queen|url=https://www.independent.ie/entertainment/scarlett-johansson-from-starlet-to-scifi-queen-35580595.html|access-date=May 6, 2018|date=April 2, 2017|last=Whitington|first=Paul|work=[[Irish_Independent|Irish Independent]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180506104441/https://www.independent.ie/entertainment/scarlett-johansson-from-starlet-to-scifi-queen-35580595.html|archive-date=May 6, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref> 她有一個同樣從事於演員事業的姐姐 Vanessa、兄長 Adrian，以及小她三分鐘的雙胞胎弟弟 Hunter<ref>{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson Shows Post-Baby Body, Walks Red Carpet With Twin|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/599412/scarlett-johansson-shows-slim-post-baby-body-again-walks-red-carpet-with-twin-brother-hunter-watch|access-date=October 9, 2017|date=November 19, 2014|publisher=[[E!_News|E! News]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170719143043/http://www.eonline.com/news/599412/scarlett-johansson-shows-slim-post-baby-body-again-walks-red-carpet-with-twin-brother-hunter-watch|archive-date=July 19, 2017|last1=Heller|first1=Corinne|url-status=live}}</ref>，另外還有一個同父異母兄 Christian，出生於她父親的第一段婚姻。她擁有美國和丹麥雙重國籍。<ref name="recordd2">{{cite news|last=Rehlin|first=Gunnar|title=Scarlett Johansson: Scandinavia is part of my heritage|work=[[Scandinavian_Traveler|Scandinavian Traveler]]|date=March 4, 2016|url=https://scandinaviantraveler.com/dk/node/4817|access-date=March 3, 2017|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303201738/https://scandinaviantraveler.com/dk/node/4817|archive-date=March 3, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Quinn|first1=Ben|title=Mary Stuart reigns again – in Ireland|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2008/apr/27/scotland.ireland|access-date=October 5, 2017|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=April 26, 2008|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006012532/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2008/apr/27/scotland.ireland|archive-date=October 6, 2017}}</ref> 她由 2017 年美國[[公共廣播電視公司|公共廣播電視公司]]的 ''Finding Your Roots'' 節目內容得知，外曾祖父的家族在[[華沙猶太人區|華沙猶太人區]]的大屠殺期間死亡。<ref>{{cite web|title=Watching 'Finding Your Roots,' family learns they are related to Scarlett Johansson|url=https://www.jweekly.com/2017/11/03/watching-finding-roots-family-learns-related-scarlett-johansson/|access-date=March 30, 2021|date=November 3, 2017|last=Schleier|first=Curt|website=The Jewish News of Northern California|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210715032339/https://www.jweekly.com/2017/11/03/watching-finding-roots-family-learns-related-scarlett-johansson/|archive-date=July 15, 2021|url-status=live}}</ref>

她就讀於曼哈頓[[格林尼治村|格林威治村]]的41[[公立學校|公立學校]]。<ref>{{cite news|title=Scoopy's Notebook|work=[[The_Villager_(Manhattan)|The Villager]]|url=https://www.thevillager.com/2008/06/scoopys-notebook-222/|volume=78|number=3|date=June 18, 2008|access-date=July 28, 2009|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108143834/http://www.thevillager.com/villager_268/scoopysnotebook.html|archive-date=January 8, 2009}}</ref> 父母在她十三歲時離婚。<ref>{{cite news|title=Scarlett Johansson: Her Life So Far|url=http://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/gallery/scarlett-johansson-picture-photo-gallery|access-date=October 4, 2017|work=[[Glamour_(magazine)|Glamour]]|date=January 12, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171029182302/http://www.glamourmagazine.co.uk/gallery/scarlett-johansson-picture-photo-gallery|archive-date=October 29, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Scarlett Johansson's dad collapses|url=https://nypost.com/2011/02/25/scarlett-johanssons-dad-collapses/|access-date=October 4, 2017|work=[[New_York_Post|New York Post]]|date=February 25, 2011|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005050801/http://nypost.com/2011/02/25/scarlett-johanssons-dad-collapses/|archive-date=October 5, 2017}}</ref> 她與外祖母多蘿西·斯隆（Dorothy Sloan）特別親近，她是一名[[簿記員|簿記員]]和學校教師。他們經常在一起，喬韓森認為多蘿西是她最好的朋友。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Weiss|first1=Anthony|title=The Scarlett Grandma|url=http://www.forward.com:80/articles/the-scarlett-grandma/|access-date=October 4, 2017|work=[[The_Forward|The Forward]]|date=April 7, 2006|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061018190128/http://www.forward.com/articles/the-scarlett-grandma/|archive-date=October 18, 2006}}</ref> 她從小就對公眾演藝活動感興趣，經常為她的家人設計歌舞活動。她特別喜歡[[音樂劇|音樂劇]]和爵士手（英語：{{Link-en|Jazz hands|Jazz hands}}）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson: Actress (1984)|url=https://www.biography.com/people/scarlett-johansson-13671719|access-date=October 3, 2017|publisher=[[Biography.com|Biography.com]] ([[A&E_Networks|A&E Networks]])|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171004035020/https://www.biography.com/people/scarlett-johansson-13671719|archive-date=October 4, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="localfav2">{{cite news|url=https://www.smh.com.au/news/film/local-favourite/2007/09/16/1189881329353.html|title=Local favourite|last=Ryzik|first=Melena|date=September 17, 2007|work=[[The_Sydney_Morning_Herald|The Sydney Morning Herald]]|access-date=October 3, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170831230146/http://www.smh.com.au/news/film/local-favourite/2007/09/16/1189881329353.html|archive-date=August 31, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref> 她學習[[踢踏舞|踢踏舞]]，並表示父母支持她的職業選擇。她形容自己的童年非常普通。<ref>{{cite news|title=Scarlett Johansson: Shades of Scarlett|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/scarlett-johansson-shades-of-scarlett-221175.html|access-date=October 7, 2017|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|date=May 13, 2005|url-status=live|quote=[my childhood] was filled with things that I loved to do, and also very normal things: I lived in New York, I have a family life and went to a regular school.|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007171200/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/scarlett-johansson-shades-of-scarlett-221175.html|archive-date=October 7, 2017}}</ref>

童年時，她藉由盯著鏡中自己的模樣練習表演，希望自己就像[[茱蒂·嘉蘭|茱蒂·嘉蘭]]（英語：Judy Garland）在聖誕[[歌舞片|歌舞片]]''Meet Me in St. Louis'' 裏面那樣。<ref name="nymag">{{cite news|last1=Bhattacharya|first1=Sanjiv|title=Scarlett in Bloom|url=https://nymag.com/nymetro/shopping/fashion/spring04/n_9843/|access-date=October 3, 2017|work=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024010621/http://nymag.com/nymetro/shopping/fashion/spring04/n_9843/|archive-date=October 24, 2012}}</ref> 七歲時，當一位[[經紀公司|經紀人]]簽下她的弟弟而不是她時，她感到非常沮喪，但她後來還是決定成為一名演員。她就讀於李斯特拉斯堡戲劇學院（英語：Lee Strasberg Theatre and Film Institute）並開始參與於廣告錄影試鏡，但很快就失去興趣，她回憶道「我不想宣傳神奇麵包」。<ref name="nymag2">{{cite news|last1=Bhattacharya|first1=Sanjiv|title=Scarlett in Bloom|url=https://nymag.com/nymetro/shopping/fashion/spring04/n_9843/|access-date=October 3, 2017|work=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024010621/http://nymag.com/nymetro/shopping/fashion/spring04/n_9843/|archive-date=October 24, 2012}}</ref> 她將事業重心轉移到電影和戲劇上<ref name="peoplebio">{{cite news|title=Scarlett Johansson Biography|url=http://www.people.com/people/scarlett_johansson/biography/0,,,00.html|access-date=October 3, 2017|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110307041129/http://www.people.com/people/scarlett_johansson/biography/0,,,00.html|archive-date=March 7, 2011}}</ref>，在[[外百老匯|外百老匯]]首次演出於舞台上<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/05/16/theater/theaterspecial/16scarlett.html|title=Definitely Didn't Get Lost in Translation|last=Isherwood|first=Charles|date=May 12, 2010|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|access-date=March 31, 2014|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140410150006/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/05/16/theater/theaterspecial/16scarlett.html|archive-date=April 10, 2014}}</ref>，在該劇目中，她有兩段演出。<ref name="peoplebio" />

==演員生涯==

===早期===
幼年時期的喬韓森便表現出了對表演的興趣，她這樣說道<ref name="c">{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson: A new Bacall?|url=http://www.today.com/id/3678179/ns/today-today_entertainment/t/scarlett-johansson-new-bacall/#.U1uTNNITX55|publisher=The Associated Press|accessdate=2014-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331174209/http://www.today.com/id/3678179/ns/today-today_entertainment/t/scarlett-johansson-new-bacall/#.U1uTNNITX55|archive-date=2014-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>：

<blockquote>我一直很喜歡-{表}-演……就像有的小孩喜歡學樂器，而我喜歡當大演員。於是就有人建議我母親帶我找找演藝中介。</blockquote>

她母親很早就帶她去各處試鏡<ref>{{cite journal|author=James Kaplan|title=More Than A Pretty Face|journal=Parade Magazine|date=2007-03-11|year=2007|pages=6-8}}</ref>，從7歲起參與各種商業廣告試鏡，但屢次遭到拒絕<ref name="c" />，並對此失去興趣；她的母親和她開始將目標轉向電影領域<ref name="people" />。1994年，9歲的她在科幻喜劇電影《{{link-en|浪子保鏢|North (1994 film)}}》中首次登上螢幕，飾演{{link-en|約翰·瑞得|John Ritter}}的女兒<ref name="people">{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson Biography|url=http://www.people.com/people/scarlett_johansson/biography/0,,,00.html|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|accessdate=2014-04-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65NhxY7zr?url=http://www.people.com/people/scarlett_johansson/biography/0,,,00.html|archive-date=2012-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之後她嘗試了幾個小角色：在1995年的電影《{{Link-en|正當防衛 (電影)|Just Cause (film)|正當防衛}}》中，她扮演[[肖恩·康納利|肖恩·康納利]]的女兒，然後參演1996年電影《{{link-en|愛在布魯克林橋|If Lucy Fell}}》，隨後，在電影《{{link-en|曼妮姐妹|Manny & Lo}}》中，她飾演了女孩阿曼達（Amanda），由此獲得了各方贊譽，以及美國[[獨立精神獎|獨立精神獎]]最佳女主角的提名。曾有人如此評論：「（這部電影）逐漸為人們所喜愛，多半是因為史嘉蕾·喬韓森的魅力<ref>{{cite news|title=Many things to like about "Manny & Lo'|first=Barbara|last=Shulgasser|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/e/a/1996/08/09/WEEKEND6031.dtl|work=San Francisco Chronicle|date=1996-08-09|accessdate=2014-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100413072341/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fe%2Fa%2F1996%2F08%2F09%2FWEEKEND6031.dtl|archive-date=2010-04-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」此外，《[[舊金山紀事報|舊金山紀事報]]》評論員米克·拉夏爾如此評論她的「平和氣質」：「未來，她將不再是個青春少女，但若仍能保持這份氣質，她就會成為一位重要的女演員<ref>{{cite news|title=Two Girls, a Condo and One Kidnapped Mom|work=San Francisco Chronicle|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/1996/08/09/DD66424.DTL|date=1996-08-09|accessdate=2009-07-26|first=Mick|last=Lasalle|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20041225110351/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F1996%2F08%2F09%2FDD66424.DTL|archive-date=2004-12-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」

1997年於電影《{{Link-en|秋 (1997年电影)|Fall (1997 film)|秋}}》和《[[小鬼当家3|小鬼当家3]]》中飾演一些小角色後，喬韓森因電影《[[輕聲細語|輕聲細語]]》受到廣泛注目<ref name="people" />，也因此當選芝加哥電影評人協會「最有前途女演員」<ref name="CFCA CS-T">{{cite news|url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CSTB&p_theme=cstb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB423E8C6BDEF67&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|title=Chicago critics list best films|date=1999-01-19|work=Chicago Sun-Times|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110609123114/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CSTB&p_theme=cstb&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB423E8C6BDEF67&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM|archive-date=2011-06-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="IMDB-Awards">{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0424060/awards|title=Scarlett Johansson — Awards|publisher=[[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]]|accessdate=2014-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140718104325/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0424060/awards|archive-date=2014-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1999年，她參演《{{link-en|他不笨它是我的心肝寶貝|My Brother the Pig}}》，同年，她還出現在[[曼迪·穆爾|曼迪·穆爾]]的單曲《糖》中<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,488747,00.html|title=He's Just Not That into You Cast: Then & Now|publisher=Fox News|date=2009-02-06|accessdate=2014-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090822130212/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,488747,00.html|archive-date=2009-08-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2001年她參演[[科恩兄弟|科恩兄弟]]電影《{{link-en|缺席的人|The Man Who Wasn't There}}》。而同年的《[[黐孖妹|黐孖妹]]》最終成為她的成名之作，她因此廣獲贊譽<ref>{{cite news|title=Scarlett Johansson – 'Ghost World'|work=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2014-04-26|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/music/la-et-bio-sjohansson-pg,0,7027798.photogallery|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100412174758/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/music/la-et-bio-sjohansson-pg,0,7027798.photogallery|archive-date=2010-04-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有人評論：「她具有與其年齡不相符的敏感和天賦」<ref>{{cite news|first=Marjorie|last=Baumgarten|title=Ghost World|work={{Link-en|Austin Chronicle|Austin Chronicle}}|url=http://www.austinchronicle.com/gyrobase/Calendar/Film?Film=oid%3A141399|date=2001-08-24|accessdate=2014-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070805075532/http://www.austinchronicle.com/gyrobase/Calendar/Film?Film=oid%3A141399|archive-date=2007-08-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>，只可惜這部電影未能取得票房成功<ref>{{cite web|title=Ghost World (2001)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghost_world|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812201211/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghost_world/|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/video/titles/ghostworld|title=Ghost World|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2009-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804075304/http://www.metacritic.com/video/titles/ghostworld|archive-date=2009-08-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后在2002年，喬韓森在電影《[[八腳怪|八腳怪]]》又飾演一個小角色<ref>{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson in 'Eight Legged Freaks'|url=http://www.hollywood.com/videos/interview/5630750/Scarlett_Johansson_in_Eight_Legged_Freaks|publisher=Hollywood.com|accessdate=2014-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331163127/http://www.hollywood.com/videos/interview/5630750/Scarlett_Johansson_in_Eight_Legged_Freaks|archive-date=2014-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 转型 ===
[[File:Scarlett_Johansson_2003.jpg|thumb]]，参与电影《[[画意私情|画意私情]]》首映。]]
2003年，约翰逊饰演了两个成人角色，自此不再饰演青少年角色<ref name="UtusanAdultRoles">{{cite web|url=http://www.utusan.com.my/utusan/info.asp?y=2003&dt=0906&pub=Utusan_Express&sec=Entertainment&pg=en_10.htm|title=Toronto film fest puts on the ritz with promising movie lineup|date=2003-06-09|work=Utusan Malaysia|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110617031627/http://www.utusan.com.my/utusan/info.asp?y=2003&dt=0906&pub=Utusan_Express&sec=Entertainment&pg=en_10.htm|archive-date=2011-06-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[索菲亚·科波拉|索菲亚·科波拉]]的电影《[[迷失东京|迷失东京]]》中，她饰演夏洛蒂（{{lang|en|Charlotte}}），一个懒散、孤单的年轻妻子，并与[[比尔·莫瑞|比尔·莫瑞]]展开对手戏<ref>{{cite web|title=Lost in Translation|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/lostintranslation|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100512185004/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/lostintranslation|archive-date=2010-05-12|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Lost in Translation (2003)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lost_in_translation|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703225602/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lost_in_translation/|archive-date=2014-07-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影评人[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]称他很喜欢这部电影，并用「十分漂亮」（{{lang|en|wonderful}}）形容二人的表演<ref>{{cite news|last=Ebert|first=Roger|title=Lost in Translation|work=Chicago Sun-Times|date=2003-09-12|url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20030912/REVIEWS/309120302/1023|accessdate=2014-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110104191510/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20030912%2FREVIEWS%2F309120302%2F1023|archive-date=2011-01-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》评论约翰逊具有「令人愉悦、平静的沉着气质」<ref>{{cite news|last=Schwarzbaum|first=Lisa|title=Lost in Translation|work=[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]|date=2003-09-10|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,479937,00.html|accessdate=2014-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427094550/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,479937,00.html|archive-date=2009-04-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》写道：「在她十八岁这年，这位女演员却演好了一个25岁的女性……约翰逊还不是比尔·莫瑞那样能力出众的演员，但是索菲亚·科波拉导演将简单和好奇心设定为人物性格核心，巧妙地避开了这一问题<ref>{{cite news|last=Mitchell|first=Elvis|title=An American in Japan, Making a Connection|work=New York Times|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2003/09/12/movies/film-review-an-american-in-japan-making-a-connection.html?pagewanted=all|date=2003-09-12|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004515/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/09/12/movies/film-review-an-american-in-japan-making-a-connection.html?pagewanted=all|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」约翰逊因这部影片获得[[英國電影學院獎最佳女主角|英國電影學院獎最佳女主角]]和[[金球奖|金球奖]]最佳女主角的提名<ref name=GGlobes>{{cite web|title=HFPA - Scarlett Johansson  4 Nominations|url=http://www.hfpa.org/browse/?param=/member/30173|publisher=Hollywood Foreign Press Association|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220214714/http://www.hfpa.org/browse/?param=%2Fmember%2F30173|archive-date=2014-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=GG2003>{{cite web|title=Globes high on 'Cold Mountain'|url=http://articles.cnn.com/2003-12-18/entertainment/globe.noms_1_screenplay-nominations-tv-comedy-series-pearl-earring?_s=PM:SHOWBIZ|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2014-07-08|date=2003-12-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003081904/http://articles.cnn.com/2003-12-18/entertainment/globe.noms_1_screenplay-nominations-tv-comedy-series-pearl-earring?_s=PM:SHOWBIZ|archivedate=2012-10-03}}</ref>，还得到几个影评组织的提名，包括[[美国广播影评人协会|美国广播影评人协会]]最佳女配角<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120904224937/http://www.bfca.org/ccawards/2003.php |archivedate=2012-09-04 |title=The 9th Critics' Choice Awards Winners and Nominations |url=http://www.bfca.org/ccawards/2003.php |publisher=Broadcast Film Critics Association |accessdate=2014-07-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>和[[芝加哥影评人协会奖最佳女主角|芝加哥影评人协会奖最佳女主角]]<ref name="nytawards">{{cite news|title=Scarlett Johansson profile|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/person/200222/Scarlett-Johansson/awards|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131008044051/http://movies.nytimes.com/person/200222/Scarlett-Johansson/awards|archive-date=2013-10-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

十八岁时，约翰逊还在{{link-en|彼得·韦伯|Peter Webber}}的《[[戴珍珠耳環的少女_(电影)|戴珍珠耳环的少女]]》一片中饰演葛利叶（{{lang|en|Griet}}）。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》称赞道：「她正经历事业的丰年，奥斯卡奖的评委们应该注意到这一点<ref>{{cite news|first=Claudia|last=Puig|title=This 'Pearl' is of great value|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2003-12-11-pearl-earring_x.htm|date=2003-12-11|accessdate=2009-07-29|work=USA Today|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090331234906/http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2003-12-11-pearl-earring_x.htm|archive-date=2009-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」在给《[[纽约客|纽约客]]》的评论中，影评人{{link-en|安东尼·莱恩|Anthony Lane}}说道：「让韦伯的电影鲜活起来的是背景安排中的张力，以及最重要的，约翰逊的出现。她一般不说话，在荧幕上表情近乎平淡，但她却在等待着某种激情，以此她可以唤来一次特写，并在镜头前怒放。这是她的电影，不是主角弗美尔的，完全不是<ref>{{cite journal|first=Anthony|last=Lane|title=Girl with a Pearl Earring|work=The New Yorker|url=http://www.newyorker.com/arts/reviews/film/girl_with_a_pearl_earring_webber｜archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20131213024444/http://www.newyorker.com/arts/reviews/film/girl_with_a_pearl_earring_webber|archivedate=2013-12-13|date=2003-12-22|accessdate=2009-07-29}}</ref>。」影评人{{link-en|欧文·格雷伯曼|Owen Gleiberman}}为《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》撰文时如此评论她「几乎无声的表演」：「在她脸上，恐惧、无辜、好奇和性欲交替出现，互相影响，这是极其戏剧化的<ref>{{cite journal |first=Owen |last=Gleiberman |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2003/12/03/girl-pearl-earring |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402124334/http://www.ew.com/article/2003/12/03/girl-pearl-earring |archivedate=2015-04-02 |title=Girl With a Pearl Earring (2003) |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2003-12-03 |accessdate=2014-05-04 |deadurl=yes |journal= }}</ref>。」因为该片，她获得了[[金球奖剧情类电影最佳女主角|金球奖剧情类电影最佳女主角]]提名<ref name=GGlobes />和英国电影学院最佳女主角提名，也被[[伦敦影评人协会|伦敦影评人协会]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Crowe Leads Race for London Critics' Awards |publisher=Contact Music |url=http://www.contactmusic.com/new/xmlfeed.nsf/mndwebpages/crowe%20leads%20race%20for%20london%20critics.%20awards |date=2004-01-05 |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716233015/http://www.contactmusic.com/russell-crowe/news/crowe-leads-race-for-london-critics.-awards |archivedate=2015-07-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>和[[菲尼克斯影评人协会|菲尼克斯影评人协会]]提名最佳女演员。

2004年6月，约翰逊受邀加入[[美国电影艺术与科学学会|美国电影艺术与科学学会]]<ref name="Oscars">{{cite news |url=http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2004/04.06.28.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080111195816/http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2004/04.06.28.html |archivedate=2008-01-11 |title=Academy Invites 127 to Membership |publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |date=2004-06-28 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2014-07-05 }}</ref>。同年，她或配音或参演了五部影片：《[[海绵宝宝电影版|海绵宝宝电影版]]》、《[[美丽诱惑|美丽诱惑]]》、《{{link-en|献给你的情歌|A Love Song for Bobby Long}}》、《{{Link-en|极速A计划|The Perfect Score}}》和《{{link-en|大公司小老板|In Good Company}}》。其中《美丽诱惑》，改编自[[奥斯卡·王尔德|奥斯卡·王尔德]]的《[[温夫人的扇子|温夫人的扇子]]》，在美国限量发行，却在票房<ref>{{cite web|title=A Good Woman|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=goodwoman.htm|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714193527/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=goodwoman.htm|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>和口碑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/good_woman|title=A Good Woman|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821021644/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/good_woman/|archive-date=2014-08-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>上双双失败，影片被《纽约时报》评为「拙劣可笑的好莱坞式荧幕改编」、「极度痛苦地割裂了影片中的英国演员和美国大牌，前者恰如其分地表达了王尔德的意图，后者却与王尔德式的英语毫无瓜葛<ref>{{cite news|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2006/02/03/movies/03woma.html|title=A Good Woman (2004)|work=The New York Times|date=2006-02-03|accessdate=2014-07-08|first=Stephen|last=Holden|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100610084456/http://movies.nytimes.com/2006/02/03/movies/03woma.html|archive-date=2010-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」少年盗窃片《极速A计划》饱受批评<ref>{{cite web|title=The Perfect Score (2004)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/perfect_score|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814201216/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/perfect_score/|archive-date=2014-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，浪漫爱情喜剧《大公司小老板》获得口碑票房双丰收<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in_good_company|title=In Good Company (2004)|accessdate=2014-07-08|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814192550/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in_good_company/|archive-date=2014-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而黑色风格的南部剧情片《献给你的情歌》为她赢得了第三个金球奖提名<ref name=GGlobes />。

===2005–2007年===
[[File:Scarlett_Johansson.jpg|thumb]]》的片场]]
2005年7月，约翰逊与[[伊旺·麥奎格|伊旺·麥奎格]]搭档出演[[迈克尔·贝|迈克尔·贝]]的科幻片《[[绝地再生|绝地再生]]》：她一人分饰两角，莎拉·乔丹（{{lang|en|Sarah Jordan}}）和她的克隆人（{{lang|en|Jordan Two Delta}}）。影片在商业上十分失败<ref name="BOM$">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=1854&p=.htm|title=Island Deserted, Chocolate Factory, Wedding Take Cake|last=Gray|first=Brandon|date=2005-07-25|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140710164738/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=1854&p=.htm|archive-date=2014-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=The Island (2005) |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=island05.htm |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090723024226/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=island05.htm |archive-date=2009-07-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，评论界也毁誉参半<ref>{{cite web|title=The Island (2005)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/island|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090304223911/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/island/|archive-date=2009-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=The Island |url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/island?q=The%20Island |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100413154356/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/island?q=The%20Island |archive-date=2010-04-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。与之相比，她在[[伍迪·艾伦|伍迪·艾伦]]的电影《[[赛末点|赛末点]]》中的表现却广受好评。《纽约时报》说道：「约翰逊和雷·麦耶斯竭力成就了伍迪·艾伦电影长期以来最好的表演，避免了伍迪·艾伦的剧本{{里}}强加的调皮和情感疏离<ref>{{cite news |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2005/12/28/movies/28matc.html?_r=1 |title=Match Point (2005) |first=A. O. |last=Scott |work=The New York Times |date=2005-12-28 |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523225436/http://movies.nytimes.com/2005/12/28/movies/28matc.html?_r=1 |archive-date=2013-05-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」由此，约翰逊获得了她第四个金球奖提名<ref name=GGlobes />，以及一个[[芝加哥影评人协会奖最佳女配角|芝加哥影评人协会奖最佳女配角]]提名<ref name="nytawards" />。

她与伍迪·艾伦另一次合作是电影《{{link-en|独家新闻|Scoop (2006 film)}}》，片中她饰演一位女大学生，并与[[休·杰克曼|休·杰克曼]]展开对手戏。影片票房不错<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=scoop.htm|title=Scoop|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090727003003/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=scoop.htm|archive-date=2009-07-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但口碑却褒贬参半<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scoop|title=Scoop (2006)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090215000005/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/scoop/|archive-date=2009-02-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/scoop|title=Scoop|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100521045730/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/scoop|archive-date=2010-05-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，她参演了[[布赖恩·德帕尔马|布赖恩·德帕尔马]]的电影《[[黑色大丽花_(电影)|黑色大丽花]]》，一部拍摄于[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]和[[保加利亚|保加利亚]]的[[黑色电影|黑色电影]]。约翰逊随后亲口承认她是德帕尔马的粉丝，虽然自觉「身材上不合适」于片中角色，却一直渴望在这部影片中与德帕尔马合作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://movies.about.com/od/theblackdahlia/a/dahliasj091306.htm|publisher=About.com|title=Scarlett Johansson Talks About The Black Dahlia|last=Murray|first=Rebecca|year=2006|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213004251/http://movies.about.com/od/theblackdahlia/a/dahliasj091306.htm|archive-date=2013-12-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

随后，她在[[克里斯托弗·诺兰|克里斯托弗·诺兰]]的影片《[[頂尖對決|頂尖對決]]》中饰演了一个配角，再一次与[[休·杰克曼|休·杰克曼]]合作，此番又加入了英国男星[[克里斯琴·贝尔|克里斯琴·贝尔]]。诺兰认为，约翰逊具有一种「暧昧迷离、遮掩朦胧的气质」<ref name="esquire">{{cite news|title=Scarlett Johansson Is the Sexiest Woman Alive, 2006|url=http://www.esquire.com/women/the-sexiest-woman-alive/scarlett-johansson-pics|work=Esquire|first=A.J.|last=Jacobs|date=2006-10-31|access-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004443/http://www.esquire.com/women/the-sexiest-woman-alive/scarlett-johansson-pics|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因此他「很渴望」由她饰演那一角色<ref name="casting">{{cite news|first=Chris|last=Carle|title=Casting The Prestige|publisher=IGN|date=2006-10-12|url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/738/738782p1.html|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090903025734/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/738/738782p1.html|archive-date=2009-09-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。约翰逊这样评价诺兰导演：「我热爱与他合作，他有着难以置信的专注力和动力，他关注表演的每个细节。」<ref>{{cite web|last=Fischer|first=Paul|title=Interview: Scarlett Johansson for "Scoop"|url=http://www.darkhorizons.com/features/1039/scarlett-johansson-for-scoop|publisher=Dark Horizons|date=2006-07-26|access-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219140636/http://www.darkhorizons.com/features/1039/scarlett-johansson-for-scoop|archive-date=2014-02-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这部影片也获得了口碑评论<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/prestige|title=The Prestige (2006)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090214233227/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/prestige|archive-date=2009-02-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>和世界范围内票房<ref>{{cite web|title=The Prestige|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=prestige.htm|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090621000309/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=prestige.htm|archive-date=2009-06-21|dead-url=no}}</ref> 的双丰收。[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]称赞该片是一部「成熟的、刺激感官的佳作」<ref>{{cite web|first=Kenneth|last=Turan|title=The Prestige|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2006/oct/20/entertainment/et-prestige20|date=2006-10-20|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814051743/http://articles.latimes.com/2006/oct/20/entertainment/et-prestige20|archive-date=2016-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年，她还出演了一部短片《若誓言永恒》（{{lang|en|''When The Deal Goes Down''}}），由[[贝尼特·米勒|贝尼特·米勒]]执导，片名取自[[鲍勃·迪伦|鲍勃·迪伦]]的同名歌曲，旨在推广迪伦的新专辑《{{link-en|Modern Times (专辑)|Modern Times (Bob Dylan album)|Modern Times}}》<ref>{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson Stars in 'When The Deal Goes Down' Film Directed by Bennett Miller Set to New Bob Dylan Song|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/scarlett-johansson-stars-in-when-the-deal-goes-down-film-directed-by-bennett-miller-set-to-new-bob-dylan-song-56282272.html|publisher=PR Newswire|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331174217/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/scarlett-johansson-stars-in-when-the-deal-goes-down-film-directed-by-bennett-miller-set-to-new-bob-dylan-song-56282272.html|archive-date=2014-03-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2007年，约翰逊与[[劳拉·琳尼|劳拉·琳尼]]一道出演了《[[褓姆日记|褓姆日记]]》。影片票房不尽如人意<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=nannydiaries.htm|title=The Nanny Diaries|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906005207/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=nannydiaries.htm|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，口碑上更饱受批评<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nanny_diaries|title=The Nanny Diaries (2007)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140710225344/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nanny_diaries/|archive-date=2014-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。对约翰逊的评论则有好有坏，[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]杂志说：“（她）饰演了一个很有魅力女主角。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117934447.html?categoryid=31&cs=1|title=The Nanny Diaries|first=Lael|last=Loewenstein|work=Variety|date=2007-08-17|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004923/http://variety.com/2007/film/reviews/the-nanny-diaries-1200557099/|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>”[[纽约客|纽约客]]杂志则批评她看上去“除去迷茫，别无他物”，却“又竭力为表演赋予真实的情感核心<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newyorker.com/arts/critics/cinema/2007/09/03/070903crci_cinema_denby|title=Eastern, Western|first=David|last=Denby|work=The New Yorker|date=2007-09-03|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5msSPZ7Ou?url=http://www.newyorker.com/arts/critics/cinema/2007/09/03/070903crci_cinema_denby|archive-date=2010-01-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

===2008年至今===
2008年，斯嘉丽·约翰逊与[[娜塔莉·波特曼|娜塔莉·波特曼]]和[[埃里克·巴纳|埃里克·巴纳]]合作，主演了影片《[[華麗孽緣|華麗孽緣]]》<ref name="mweb">{{cite news|publisher=MovieWeb|title=Scarlett Johansson Is The Other Boleyn Girl|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/NEc3MlhhG6Qzfg|accessdate=2006-07-18|date=2006-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081003191241/http://www.movieweb.com/news/NEc3MlhhG6Qzfg|archive-date=2008-10-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>，影片毁誉参半<ref>{{cite web|title=The Other Boleyn Girl|url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/otherboleyngirl|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090524081240/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/otherboleyngirl/|archive-date=2009-05-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.rottentomatoes.com/m/other_boleyn_girl|title=The Other Boleyn Girl (2008)|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090627174425/http://uk.rottentomatoes.com/m/other_boleyn_girl/|archive-date=2009-06-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影评人[[彼得·特拉维斯|彼得·特拉维斯]]说：“影片发展一路跌跌撞撞，令人沮丧”，但他对两位女主评价甚高，“但娜塔莉·波特曼和斯嘉丽·约翰逊配合堪称完美，后者让我们看到，智力和聪慧才是这些漂亮女孩的真正内核。<ref>{{cite web|last=Travers|first=Peter|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/the-other-boleyn-girl-20080320|title=Other Boleyn Girl|work=Rolling Stone|date=2008-03-28|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714140542/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/the-other-boleyn-girl-20080320|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>”

其后，斯嘉丽·约翰逊第三次出现在伍迪·艾伦的影片中，这次是《[[午夜巴塞罗那|午夜巴塞罗那]]》，拍摄于西班牙<ref name="usatoday807">{{cite news|last=Stinson|first=Jeffrey|title=Hollywood enters the era of Scarlett Johansson|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2007-08-21-scarlett-johansson-cover_N.htm|work=USA Today|date=2007-08-22|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111214114822/http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2007-08-21-scarlett-johansson-cover_N.htm|archive-date=2011-12-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并与[[查維爾·巴頓|查維爾·巴頓]]和[[佩内洛普·克鲁兹|佩内洛普·克鲁兹]]同场飙戏。该片成为伍迪·艾伦最卖座的电影之一，同时也被许多影片人列为年度十佳<ref>{{cite web|title=Vicky Cristina Barcelona|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=vickycristinabarcelona.htm|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090924084515/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=vickycristinabarcelona.htm|archive-date=2009-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

随后她参演了[[弗兰克·米勒|弗兰克·米勒]]的电影《{{link-en|鬼魂 (电影)|The Spirit (film)|鬼魂}}》，扮演了一位[[蛇蝎美人|蛇蝎美人]]。影片受到的评论多为负面<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_spirit|title=The Spirit (2008)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090321173043/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_spirit/|archive-date=2009-03-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2009年，约翰逊在电影《[[他其實沒那麼喜歡妳|他其實沒那麼喜歡妳]]》中与[[詹妮弗·康纳利|詹妮弗·康纳利]]、[[布莱德利·库珀|布莱德利·库珀]]、[[德鲁·巴里莫尔|德鲁·巴里莫尔]]合作，饰演一位名叫安娜的瑜伽教练。影片在票房上颇为成功<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=hesjustnotthatintoyou.htm|title=He's Just Not That into You|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090809094956/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=hesjustnotthatintoyou.htm|archive-date=2009-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>，唯独口碑平平<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/hesjustnot|title=He's Just Not That into You|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100424221126/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/hesjustnot|archive-date=2010-04-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=He's Just Not That into You (2009)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hes_just_not_that_into_you|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090529125520/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hes_just_not_that_into_you/|archive-date=2009-05-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[File:Don_Jon_09_(9725727751)_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]]]
2009年3月，[[艾米莉·布朗特|艾米莉·布朗特]]拒绝邀片后<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2110823/Emily-Blunt-turned-lead-females-roles-Iron-Man-2-Captain-America.html|work=Daily Mail|date=2012-03-06|accessdate=2014-07-08|last=Fitzmaurice|first=Sarah|title='I'd rather play James Bond': Emily Blunt on why she turned down lead females roles in Iron Man 2 and Captain America|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004523/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2110823/Emily-Blunt-turned-lead-females-roles-Iron-Man-2-Captain-America.html|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，约翰逊与《[[钢铁侠2|钢铁侠2]]》签约，在其中饰演“[[黑寡婦_(娜塔莉亞·羅曼諾娃)|黑寡妇]]”一角<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news-briefs.ew.com/2009/03/12/scarlett-johans |title=Iron Man 2: Scarlett Johansson cast as Black Widow |first=Jeremy |last=Medina |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2009-03-12 |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108212540/http://news-briefs.ew.com/2009/03/12/scarlett-johans/ |archivedate=2014-01-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。影片2010年5月上映<ref name="comic">{{cite web |first=Nicole |last=Sperling |title=Iron Man 2 crew returns to Comic-Con as conquering heroes and sets off a whole new buzz bomb |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2009-07-26 |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2009/07/26/iron-man-2-comiccon |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716233628/http://www.ew.com/article/2009/07/26/iron-man-2-comiccon |archivedate=2015-07-16 |accessdate=2015-07-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，取得票房佳绩的同时<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=ironman2.htm|title=Iron Man 2|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602032832/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=ironman2.htm|archive-date=2017-06-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也在评论界广受好评<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/iron_man_2|title=Iron Man 2|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120625102736/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/iron_man_2/|archive-date=2012-06-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，她又参演《[[我家买了动物园|我家买了动物园]]》一片<ref>{{cite news|title=《我家买了动物园》首映 斯嘉丽 马特·达蒙亲密亮相|url=http://gb.cri.cn/27564/2011/12/14/3465s3477189.htm|accessdate=2014-06-30|newspaper=国际在线|date=2011-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714121110/http://gb.cri.cn/27564/2011/12/14/3465s3477189.htm|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，饰演动物管理员凯利一角。该片同样好评连连<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/we_bought_a_zoo|title=We Bought a Zoo|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120630075847/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/we_bought_a_zoo/|archive-date=2012-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年，她在《[[復仇者聯盟_(電影)|复仇者联盟]]》中再次饰演黑寡妇，影片收获赞誉<ref>{{cite web|title=Marvel's The Avengers (2012)|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/marvels_the_avengers|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120630071806/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/marvels_the_avengers/|archive-date=2012-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>，票房上更是赚得盆满钵满，一举成为[[最高电影票房收入列表|世界电影史上票房收入第三高]]的电影（仅次于《[[阿凡达|阿凡达]]》和《[[泰坦尼克号_(1997年电影)|泰坦尼克号]]》）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-milestone-avengers-number-three-332331|title=Box Office Milestone: 'The Avengers' Becomes No. 3 Pic of All Time With $1.331 Billion|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|first=Pamela|last=McClintock|date=2012-06-20|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160831205255/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-milestone-avengers-number-three-332331|archive-date=2016-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年11月，报道称斯嘉丽·约翰逊正计划她的导演首秀，影片改编自[[杜鲁门·卡波特|杜鲁门·卡-{}-波特]]的《夏日的跨越》，将由剧作家{{link-en|普瑞士坦·斯凯勒|Tristine Skyler}}编剧<ref>{{cite web|last=Labrecque|first=Jeff|title=Scarlett Johansson to direct Capote's 'Summer Crossing'|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/11/18/scarlett-johansson-direct-summer-crossing/|work=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=2014-07-08|date=2011-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140825030233/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2011/11/18/scarlett-johansson-direct-summer-crossing/|archive-date=2014-08-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertainment.time.com/2013/05/16/the-story-behind-scarlett-johanssons-directorial-debut|title=The Story Behind Scarlett Johansson’s Directorial Debut|last=Rothman|first=Lily|work=Time|date=2013-05-16|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209141831/http://entertainment.time.com/2013/05/16/the-story-behind-scarlett-johanssons-directorial-debut/|archive-date=2017-02-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=斯嘉丽甩裸照风波阴影 事业猛进将执导电影|url=http://www.chinanews.com/yl/2011/11-21/3473844.shtml|accessdate=2014-06-30|newspaper=东莞时报|date=2011-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714214357/http://www.chinanews.com/yl/2011/11-21/3473844.shtml|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，影片计划于2014年上半年开拍。2012年5月上旬，官方宣布约翰逊将在影片《[[希区柯克_(电影)|希区柯克]]》中扮演[[珍妮特·利|珍妮特·利]]。该片由{{link-en|萨沙·杰瓦西|Sacha Gervasi}}执导，讲述希区柯克1960年电影《[[驚魂記|驚魂記]]》的幕后故事<ref>{{cite news|last=Kroll|first=Justin|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118050966|title=Scarlett Johansson to star in 'Making of Psycho'|work=Variety|publisher=Reed Business Information|date=2012-03-01|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120404210722/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118050966|archive-date=2012-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Kit|first=Borys|last2=Belloni|first2=Matthew|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/scarlett-johansson-alfred-hitchcock-psycho-anthony-hopkins-296460|title=Scarlett Johansson Joins 'Making of Psycho' as Janet Leigh|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=2012-03-01|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004641/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/scarlett-johansson-alfred-hitchcock-psycho-anthony-hopkins-296460|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片2012年11月上映，有论者褒贬参半，亦有论者大加赞赏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hitchcock|title=Hitchcock|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121125004417/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hitchcock/|archive-date=2012-11-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年，约翰逊参演了[[约瑟夫·高登-莱维特|约瑟夫·高登-莱维特]]导演处女作《[[情圣囧色夫|情圣囧色夫]]》<ref>{{cite web |first=Edward |last=Davis |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/julianne-moore-joins-joseph-gordon-levitts-untitled-directorial-debut-starring-scarlett-johansson |title=Julianne Moore Joins Joseph Gordon-Levitt's Untitled Directorial Debut Starring Scarlett Johansson |date=2012-03-28 |publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]] |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004355/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/julianne-moore-joins-joseph-gordon-levitts-untitled-directorial-debut-starring-scarlett-johansson |archive-date=2014-09-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，影片首映于2013年[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Child|first=Ben|title=Joseph Gordon-Levitt directorial debut sells for $4m|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jan/22/joseph-gordon-levitt-directorial-debut|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2013-02-18|date=2013-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130126124954/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2013/jan/22/joseph-gordon-levitt-directorial-debut|archive-date=2013-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2013年9月起广泛上映。影片得到不少赞誉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/don_jon|title=Don Jon|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131001061853/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/don_jon/|archive-date=2013-10-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，斯嘉丽·约翰逊的表演被评论家们特别提及，《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》的评论称“这是她本人最好的演出之一，这位骄横跋扈、成天嚼口香糖的女孩十分出彩。<ref>{{cite web|last=Puig|first=Claudia|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/09/26/don-jon-review/2711907|title='Don Jon' weaves porn and comedy with unexpected charm|work=USA Today|date=2013-09-27|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004711/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/09/26/don-jon-review/2711907/|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>”2013年，约翰逊在电影《[[雲端情人|雲端情人]]》中顶替了{{link-en|萨曼莎·莫顿|Samantha Morton}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vulture.com/2013/06/spike-jonze-replaced-samantha-morton-with-scarjo.html|title=Exclusive: Scarlett Johansson Replaced Samantha Morton in Spike Jonze’s New Film, Her|last=Buchanan|first=Kyle|work=New York|date=2013-06-21|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102014900/http://www.vulture.com/2013/06/spike-jonze-replaced-samantha-morton-with-scarjo.html|archive-date=2014-01-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=科幻爱情片《她》突换女主角 斯嘉丽代替萨曼莎|url=http://gb.cri.cn/27564/2013/06/24/3465s4157997.htm|accessdate=2014-06-30|newspaper=电影网|date=2013-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714150638/http://gb.cri.cn/27564/2013/06/24/3465s4157997.htm|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，献声为人工智能系统萨曼莎配音<ref>{{cite news|author=西风|title=斯嘉丽提前出局金球奖 配音表演不具资格|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/2013-11-28/10134051102.shtml|accessdate=2014-06-30|newspaper=新浪娱乐|date=2013-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714185036/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/f/2013-11-28/10134051102.shtml|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影口碑良好，约翰逊的配音表演虽不露一面，却同样大获好评<ref>{{cite web|last=Foundas|first=Scott|title=Film Review: ‘Her’|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/film-review-her-1200710608/|work=[[Variety_(magazine){{!}}Variety|Variety (magazine){{!}}Variety]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703230247/http://variety.com/2013/film/reviews/film-review-her-1200710608/|archive-date=2014-07-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Corliss|first=Richard|title=Spike Jonze’s her: Falling in Love With the IT Girl  Read more: Spike Jonze's 'her': Falling in Love With the IT Girl|url=http://entertainment.time.com/2013/10/12/spike-jonzes-her-falling-in-love-with-the-it-girl/|work=[[Time_(magazine){{!}}Time|Time (magazine){{!}}Time]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170309042627/http://entertainment.time.com/2013/10/12/spike-jonzes-her-falling-in-love-with-the-it-girl/|archive-date=2017-03-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并凭借此片获得了第8届罗马电影节最佳女演员奖。

2010年11月，约翰逊参演影片《[[皮囊之下|皮囊之下]]》，影片改编自[[米歇爾·法柏|米歇爾·法柏]]的同名小说，由{{link-en|乔纳森・格雷泽|Jonathan Glazer}}执导<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/blogs/heat-vision/scarlett-johansson-play-alien-seductress-35110|title=Scarlett Johansson to Play Alien Seductress in 'Under the Skin'|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|first=Borys|last=Kit|date=2010-11-03|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004937/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/blogs/heat-vision/scarlett-johansson-play-alien-seductress-35110|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。片中她曾一丝不挂，全裸出镜<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/online/oscars/2013/08/scarlett-johansson-under-the-skin-trailer|title=Alien Scarlett Johansson Seduces Scottish Men (but Not Early Critics) in Under the Skin, Her Sexy Hitchhiker Movie|work=[[Vanity_Fair_(magazine)|Vanity Fair]]|first=Julie|last=Miller|date=2013-09-03|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130905205257/http://www.vanityfair.com/online/oscars/2013/08/scarlett-johansson-under-the-skin-trailer|archive-date=2013-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，影片在美国上映，获得好评<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/under_the_skin_2013/|title=Under the Skin (2013)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140404153404/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/under_the_skin_2013/|archive-date=2014-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>，约翰逊的表演也得到赞誉<ref>{{cite news|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/review-jonathan-glazers-seductive-girl-who-fell-to-earth-pic-under-the-skin-starring-scarlett-johansson-20140401|title=Review: Jonathan Glazer's Seductive Girl-Who-Fell-To-Earth Pic 'Under The Skin' Starring Scarlett Johansson|work=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|first=Chris|last=Willman|date=2014-04-01|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140827210608/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/review-jonathan-glazers-seductive-girl-who-fell-to-earth-pic-under-the-skin-starring-scarlett-johansson-20140401|archive-date=2014-08-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Travers|first=Peter|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/under-the-skin-20140403|title=Under the Skin|work=Rolling Stone|date=2014-04-03|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705154658/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/under-the-skin-20140403|archive-date=2014-07-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年5月2日，第2470位大名被鑲在[[好萊塢星光大道|好萊塢星光大道]](Hollywood Walk of Fame)上，對電影產業有所貢獻。

约翰逊在《[[美国队长2|美国队长2]]》中再次饰演黑寡妇<ref name="WinterSoldier"/>，并与男星[[克里斯·埃文斯|克里斯·埃文斯]]合作。影片2014年上映后获得好评<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/captain_america_the_winter_soldier_2014/|title=Captain America: The Winter Soldier (2014)|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150726040718/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/captain_america_the_winter_soldier_2014/|archive-date=2015-07-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，在2014年上映的影片《[[厨师_(电影)|厨师]]》中，她与[[乔恩·费儒|乔恩·费儒]]、[[小罗伯特·唐尼|小罗伯特·唐尼]]和[[索菲娅·维加拉|索菲娅·维加拉]]合作，并饰演莫莉一角。同年，她还主演了[[吕克·贝松|吕克·贝松]]执导的科幻动作片《[[露西_(电影)|露西]]》<ref name="hollywoodreporter2">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/scarlett-johansson-star-luc-bessons-446576|title=Scarlett Johansson to Star in Luc Besson's Latest Action Movie (Exclusive)|publisher=HollywoodReporter.com|date=2013-04-25|first=Tatiana|last=Siegel|access-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822103821/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/scarlett-johansson-star-luc-bessons-446576|archive-date=2017-08-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>，该片上映后，影評人對约翰森在影片中的表现讚譽有加<ref name="Lombardi">{{cite web|last=Lombardi|first=Ken|title="Lucy," "Hercules" both get strength from critics|work=[[CBS_News|CBS News]]|date=2014-07-25|accessdate=2014-09-08|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/lucy-hercules-both-get-strength-from-critics/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140910200221/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/lucy-hercules-both-get-strength-from-critics/|archive-date=2014-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Sims">{{cite web|last=Sims|first=David|title=Is 'Lucy' Being Criticized as Dumb Because It's About Being Smart?|publisher=[[thewire.com|thewire.com]]|date=2014-07-25|accessdate=2014-07-25|url=http://www.thewire.com/entertainment/2014/07/is-lucy-being-criticized-as-dumb-because-its-about-being-smart/375053/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140725173824/http://www.thewire.com/entertainment/2014/07/is-lucy-being-criticized-as-dumb-because-its-about-being-smart/375053/|archive-date=2014-07-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Gettell">{{cite web|last=Gettell|first=Oliver|title='Lucy': 5 reasons the Scarlett Johansson film ruled the box office|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2014-07-22|accessdate=2014-08-22|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-lucy-5-reasons-scarlett-johansson-ruled-the-box-office-20140728-story.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826153932/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/moviesnow/la-et-mn-lucy-5-reasons-scarlett-johansson-ruled-the-box-office-20140728-story.html|archive-date=2014-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref> 並在电影预算只有四千万美元下收获四亿五千八万票房。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=lucy.htm|title=Lucy (2014)|publisher=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2014-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226034709/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=lucy.htm%20|archive-date=2018-12-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年，约翰逊与《复仇者联盟》第一部原班人马合作，继续在《[[復仇者聯盟2：奧創紀元|復仇者聯盟2：奧創紀元]]》{{里}}扮演黑寡妇<ref name="Johansson2">{{cite web |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/scarlett-johansson-flaunts-curves-new-magazine-photo-shoot-article-1.1470378 |title=Scarlett Johansson flaunts curves in new magazine photo shoot, reveals details on 'The Avengers' sequel |last=Maresca |first=Rachel |work=The New York Daily News |date=2013-09-29 |accessdate=2013-09-29 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6K03pw89R?url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/scarlett-johansson-flaunts-curves-new-magazine-photo-shoot-article-1.1470378 |archivedate=2013-09-29 |deadurl=no }}</ref> ，影片中采用了特写镜头，3位特技替身演员和后期视觉效果来帮助隐藏在拍摄过程怀孕的约翰逊<ref>{{cite web |url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/07/18/avengers-age-of-ultron-scarlett-johanssons-pregnancy/ |title=How 'Avengers: Age of Ultron' will hide Scarlett Johansson's pregnancy |last=Breznican |first=Anthony |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2014-07-18 |accessdate=2014-07-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RAdLPGJO?url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/07/18/avengers-age-of-ultron-scarlett-johanssons-pregnancy/ |archivedate=2014-07-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2016年，喬韓森出演《[[美国队长3|美国队长3]]》，回歸飾演黑寡婦<ref name="JohanssonCapCW">{{cite web |url=http://www.newsarama.com/23231-black-widow-back-for-captain-america-civil-war-and-more-from-the-russos.html |title=Captain America: Civil War Directors: Black Widow Will Be Back, More |last=Arrant |first=Chris |website=Newsarama |date=2015-01-15 |accessdate=2015-01-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119212654/http://www.newsarama.com/23231-black-widow-back-for-captain-america-civil-war-and-more-from-the-russos.html |archivedate=2015-01-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

2019年，約翰遜憑著《[[婚姻故事|婚姻故事]]》的表演入圍金球獎、美國演員工會獎和英國電影學院獎，並首次獲奧斯卡獎提名，同時其在《[[兔嘲男孩|兔嘲男孩]]》的演繹也入選女配角獎，使她成為自2007年的[[凱特·布蘭琪|凱特·布蘭琪]]後，12年來首位在[[同年獲兩項奧斯卡金像獎提名演員列表|同屆奧斯卡中取得兩項演藝類別提名的演員]]。

==戏剧生涯==
约翰逊八岁时即完成了戏剧首秀，那是在[[外百老匯|外百老匯]]小剧场的一次表演，同台的还有[[伊桑·霍克|伊桑·霍克]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Isherwood|first=Charles|title=Definitely Didn’t Get Lost in Translation|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/05/16/theater/theaterspecial/16scarlett.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|publisher=New York Times|accessdate=2014-07-08|date=2010-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929044004/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/05/16/theater/theaterspecial/16scarlett.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|archive-date=2017-09-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson : People|url=http://www.people.com/people/scarlett_johansson/|publisher=People|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704181304/http://www.people.com/people/scarlett_johansson|archive-date=2014-07-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年1月，约翰逊在百老汇首秀<ref>{{cite news|title=斯嘉丽约翰松百老汇处女秀《桥头眺望》上演|url=http://news.163.com/10/0125/16/5TSUI7UL000120GU.html|accessdate=2014-06-30|newspaper=[[新华网|新华网]]|date=2010-01-25|archive-url=https://archive.is/20140703055518/http://news.163.com/10/0125/16/5TSUI7UL000120GU.html|archive-date=2014-07-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，在戏剧《{{link-en|桥头眺望|A View from the Bridge}}》中饰演凯瑟琳，剧本由[[亚瑟·米勒|亚瑟·米勒]]创作，并由{{link-en|乔治·穆舍|Gregory Mosher}}执导，与她搭档的则是[[李佛·薛伯|李佛·薛伯]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.broadway.com/buzz/scarlett-johansson-makes-her-broadway-debut-opposite-tony-winner-liev-schreiber-view-bridge/|publisher=Broadway.com|title=Scarlett Johansson to Make Her Broadway Debut Opposite Liev Schreiber in A View from the Bridge|date=2009-10-26|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100327090703/http://www.broadway.com/buzz/scarlett-johansson-makes-her-broadway-debut-opposite-tony-winner-liev-schreiber-view-bridge/|archive-date=2010-03-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于在剧中的表现，她赢得了当年[[東尼獎|東尼獎]]最佳舞台剧女配角<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/06/14/theater/theaterspecial/14tony.html?hp|work=The New York Times|title=The 64th Annual Tony Awards|date=2010-06-14|first=Patrick|last=Healy|access-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629031850/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/06/14/theater/theaterspecial/14tony.html?hp|archive-date=2014-06-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但是她的获奖却引发评论界和百老汇资深演员强烈反对，他们认为约翰逊不配获此殊荣<ref>{{cite news|title=Scarlett Johansson Slams Tony Critics: "I Worked My Ass Off"|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/entertainment/news/scarlett-johansson-i-understand-why-people-think-i-didnt-deserve-a-tony-2010236|accessdate=2014-07-02|newspaper=USWEEKLY|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150506154615/http://www.usmagazine.com/entertainment/news/scarlett-johansson-i-understand-why-people-think-i-didnt-deserve-a-tony-2010236|archive-date=2015-05-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年1月17日，约翰逊参演戏剧《[[热铁皮屋顶上的猫_(戏剧)|热铁皮屋顶上的猫]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/170231-Benjamin-Walker-Debra-Monk-and-Ciaran-Hinds-Will-Join-Scarlett-Johansson-in-Broadways-Cat-on-a-Hot-Tin-Roof |title=Benjamin Walker, Debra Monk and Ciaran Hinds Will Join Scarlett Johansson in Broadway's Cat on a Hot Tin Roof |work={{link-en|Playbill|Playbill}} |first=Adam |last=Hetrick |date=2012-09-12 |accessdate=2014-07-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130103134414/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/170231-Benjamin-Walker-Debra-Monk-and-Ciaran-Hinds-Will-Join-Scarlett-Johansson-in-Broadways-Cat-on-a-Hot-Tin-Roof |archivedate=2013-01-03 }}</ref>。她的表演在评论界毁誉参半<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.eonline.com/news/379889/scarlett-johansson-in-cat-on-a-hot-tin-roof-early-reviews-surface-critics-not-so-hot-about-broadway-revival|title=Scarlett Johansson in Cat on a Hot Tin Roof: Early Reviews Surface, Critics Not So Hot About Broadway Revival|work=E! Online|last=Grossberg|first=Josh|date=2013-01-18|accessdate=2013-01-18|archive-date=2021-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210517235103/https://www.eonline.com/news/379889/scarlett-johansson-in-cat-on-a-hot-tin-roof-early-reviews-surface-critics-not-so-hot-about-broadway-revival|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的评论称：“在导演罗布·阿什福德（{{lang|en|Rob Ashford}}）这部慢悠悠的复排剧中，斯嘉丽·约翰逊给她的角色玛吉（{{lang|en|Maggie the Cat}}）带来了暴烈的、战斗的灵魂……她展现出赢得一切决心——把丈夫诱回身边、捍卫属于他们那一份的家庭财产、并保持着一个时而颤抖的南部口音。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Geier|first=Thom|title=Cat on a Hot Tin Roof|journal=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2013-01-25|location= New York|publisher= Time Inc.|page=123}}</ref>”但纽约《[[纽约每日新闻|每日新闻]]》的评论家乔·迪兹米阿诺维奇（{{lang|en|Joe Dziemianowicz}}）则认为她的表演“惊人的单调”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/theater-review-cat-hot-tin-roof-article-1.1241257#ixzz2IKnPoxQw|title=Theater review: ‘Cat on a Hot Tin Roof’|work=The Daily News|first=Joe|last=Dziemianowicz|date=2013-01-16|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130423113720/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/theater-review-cat-hot-tin-roof-article-1.1241257#ixzz2IKnPoxQw|archive-date=2013-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==音乐生涯==
[[File:Nobel_Peace_Prize_Concert_2008_Scarlett_Johansson_Michael_Caine.jpg|thumb]]于2008年[[诺贝尔和平奖|诺贝尔和平奖]]音乐会]]

2005年，[[安德鲁·劳埃德·韦伯|安德鲁·劳埃德·韦伯]]计划重排戏剧《[[音乐之声|音乐之声]]》，并考虑让约翰逊饰演玛丽亚<ref name="Maria">{{cite news |first=James |last=Inverne |title=Lloyd Webber Wants Scarlett Johansson for London Sound of Music |url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/92834-Lloyd_Webber_Wants_Scarlett_Johansson_for_London_Sound_of_Music |accessdate=2014-06-30 |date=2005-05-09 |work=Playbill News |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090627225859/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/92834-Lloyd_Webber_Wants_Scarlett_Johansson_for_London_Sound_of_Music |archivedate=2009-06-27 }}</ref>，但该角色最终转为由新人{{link-en|康妮·费舍尔|Connie Fisher}}出演<ref name="ConnieFisher">{{cite news |title=I would never mime on stage |date=2007-08-17 |first=Karen |last=Price |url=http://icwales.icnetwork.co.uk/0900entertainment/0050artsnews/tm_headline=i-would-never-mime-on-stage&method=full&objectid=19648489&siteid=50082-name_page.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071116104907/http://icwales.icnetwork.co.uk/0900entertainment/0050artsnews/tm_headline%3Di-would-never-mime-on-stage%26method%3Dfull%26objectid%3D19648489%26siteid%3D50082-name_page.html |archivedate=2007-11-16 |accessdate=2007-08-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在2006年5月8日发行的专辑《{{link-en|意外的梦|Unexpected Dreams}}》中，约翰逊献唱了一首《[[夏日_(歌曲)|夏日]]》，这是一份好莱坞演员们演唱的慈善专辑<ref>{{cite news|title=斯嘉丽-约翰逊首张个人专辑封面公布|url=http://yule.sohu.com/20080407/n256138012.shtml|accessdate=2014-06-30|newspaper=搜狐娱乐|date=2008-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714165322/http://yule.sohu.com/20080407/n256138012.shtml|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，在2007年4月，她在[[科切拉音乐节|科切拉音乐节]]一个特别的重逢演出上与{{link-en|吉瑟斯和玛丽琴|The Jesus And Mary Chain}}乐队同台献唱<ref name="coachella">{{cite news|first=Jeff|last=Leeds|work=The New York Times|title=Coachella: Scarlett Johansson Joins Jesus and Mary Chain|url=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2007/04/28/coachella-scarlett-johansson-joins-jesus-and-mary-chain|date=2007-04-28|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070503084432/http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2007/04/28/coachella-scarlett-johansson-joins-jesus-and-mary-chain/|archive-date=2007-05-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2007年，约翰逊还在[[贾斯汀·汀布莱克|贾斯汀·汀布莱克]]的MV《[[What_Goes_Around..._Comes_Around]》中扮演女主，这份MV也在当年8月的[[MTV音乐录像带大奖|What Goes Around... Comes Around]》中扮演女主，这份MV也在当年8月的[[MTV音乐录像带大奖]]中被提名年度最佳<ref name="MTV video">{{cite news|date=2007-08-08|title=Justin Timberlake, Beyonce lead MTV Video Music Awards with 7 nods each|accessdate=2014-07-08|url=http://www.pittsburghlive.com/x/pittsburghtrib/ae/s_521050.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100119093343/http://www.pittsburghlive.com/x/pittsburghtrib/ae/s_521050.html|archive-date=2010-01-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年中，她在[[莫里斯_(路易斯安那州)|莫里斯]]录制专辑，为之工作了一整月。她创作了一首原创歌曲、翻唱了十首[[汤姆·威茨|汤姆·威茨]]的作品<ref name="localfav">{{cite news|last=Ryzik|first=Melena|title=Local favourite|work=Sydney Morning Herald|url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/film/local-favourite/2007/09/16/1189881329353.html|date=2007-09-17|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170831230146/http://www.smh.com.au/news/film/local-favourite/2007/09/16/1189881329353.html|archive-date=2017-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="foxnews">{{cite news |title=Scarlett Johansson Record Deal in the Works |first=Roger |last=Friedman |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,221001,00.html |publisher=Fox News |accessdate=2014-07-08 |date=2006-10-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061017212254/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0%2C2933%2C221001%2C00.html |archivedate=2006-10-17 }}</ref>，专辑由制作人{{link-en|戴夫·希特克|Dave Sitek}}制作，[[大卫·鲍伊|大卫·鲍伊]]<ref name="observer">{{cite news|first=Barney|last=Hoskyns|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2008/may/18/popandrock.shopping18|title=Scarlett Johansson, Anywhere I Lay My Head|work=The Observer|date=2008-05-18|accessdate=2014-07-08|location=London|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130725010716/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2008/may/18/popandrock.shopping18|archive-date=2013-07-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{lang|en|[[Yeah_Yeah_Yeahs|Yeah Yeah Yeahs]]}}<ref name="debut">{{cite news|url=http://www.boston.com/news/globe/living/articles/2007/08/04/a_johansson_debut|title=A Johansson debut|date=2007-08-07|work=The Boston Globe|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716133201/http://www.boston.com/news/globe/living/articles/2007/08/04/a_johansson_debut/|archive-date=2014-07-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>和{{lang|en|{{link-en|Celebration|Celebration (band)}}}}的乐队成员为之贡献伴唱和伴奏<ref name="Oct07">{{cite news|first=Julie|title=Scarlett Johansson: From Actress to Singer|url=http://www.clevelandleader.com/node/2612|work=Cleveland Leader|date=2007-08-29|accessdate=2014-07-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018160223/http://www.clevelandleader.com/node/2612|archivedate=2014-10-18}}</ref>，于2008年5月20日出版发行，定名为《{{lang|en|{{link-en|Anywhere I Lay My Head|Anywhere I Lay My Head}}}}》<ref>{{cite web|last=Kharas|first=Kev|title=David Bowie to guest on Scarlett Johansson's Tom Waits covers record|publisher={{Link-en|Drowned in Sound|Drowned in Sound}}|date=2008-02-14|url=http://drownedinsound.com/news/2930510|access-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906005009/http://drownedinsound.com/news/2930510|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson to Release Album in May|url=http://www.andpop.com/2008/01/09/scarlett-johansson-to-release-album-in-may/|accessdate=2008-04-22|first=Max|last=Whiteside|date=2008-01-09|publisher=andPOP|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091012035229/http://www.andpop.com/2008/01/09/scarlett-johansson-to-release-album-in-may/|archive-date=2009-10-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这份专辑收到的评论多种多样<ref>{{cite web|title=Anywhere I Lay My Head by Scarlett Johansson|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/artists/johanssonscarlett/anywhereilaymyhead|publisher=Metacritic|access-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080525225345/http://www.metacritic.com/music/artists/johanssonscarlett/anywhereilaymyhead|archive-date=2008-05-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{lang|en|[[Spin|Spin]]}}》杂志认为：“斯嘉丽·约翰逊的歌唱毫无格外引人入胜之处。<ref name="SMW">{{cite web|url=http://www.spin.com/reviews/scarlett-johansson-anywhere-i-lay-my-head-atco|title=Scarlett Johansson, 'Anywhere I Lay My Head' (ATCO) Bombshell actress coos coyly behind hipster sound sculptor.|last=Wood|first=Mikael|date=2008-05-29|publisher=Spin|accessdate=2010-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213165648/http://www.spin.com/reviews/scarlett-johansson-anywhere-i-lay-my-head-atco|archive-date=2012-02-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>”相反也有评论家称赞：“迷人得令人惊奇”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2008/may/16/popandrock2|first=Dorian|last=Lynskey|work=The Guardian|title=Scarlett Johansson, Anywhere I Lay My Head|date=2008-05-16|location=London|access-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130727144724/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2008/may/16/popandrock2|archive-date=2013-07-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>、“一份勇敢的、离经叛道的佳作”<ref name="observer"/>和“一份有着鬼魅魔力的优秀专辑”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nme.com/reviews/scarlett-johansson/9660 nme.com|first=Priya|last=Elan|title=Scarlett Johansson — Anywhere I Lay My Head|work=NME|location=UK|date=2008-05-02|accessdate=2009-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090423081735/http://www.nme.com/reviews/scarlett-johansson/9660|archive-date=2009-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《新音乐快递》杂志将之评为“2008年最佳专辑第23名”<ref>{{cite journal|title=NME's Top 50 Albums of 2008 – Year-End List|work=NME|date=2008-12-10|author=Staff}}</ref>，在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]上它则位列126名<ref>{{cite web|title=Anywhere I Lay My Head (2008)|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/278355/scarlett+johansson/chart|work=Billboard|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906005229/http://www.billboard.com/artist/278355/scarlett+johansson/chart|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。对于她的专辑，约翰逊本人说道<ref>{{cite web|first=Joshua|last=Ostroff|url=http://www.exclaim.ca/articles/multiarticlesub.aspx?csid1=122&csid2=778&fid1=31350|title=Scarlett Johansson Down in the Bayou|work=Exclaim!|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090605093208/http://www.exclaim.ca/articles/multiarticlesub.aspx?csid1=122&csid2=778&fid1=31350|archive-date=2009-06-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>：
<blockquote>我得到了这次宝贵的录音机会，并想我能唱出一份或许合乎标准的专辑，因为我不是写歌的。我是演唱者。</blockquote>
她说她“渴望拥有一片空间，在一个遥远的地方，每个人都可以做他们自己，不必关心别人的窥听和干涉。<ref>{{cite web |first=Amanda |last=Petrusich |title=Scarlett Johansson |url=http://pitchfork.com/features/interviews/6848-scarlett-johansson/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215000000/http://pitchfork.com/features/interviews/6848-scarlett-johansson/ |archivedate=2015-02-15 |publisher=Pitchfork |date=2008-05-12 |accessdate=2014-07-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>”在一次访谈中，她说她从11、12岁起就开始听汤姆·威茨的歌了<ref>{{cite web |first=Stephen |last=Mooallem |title=Scarlett Johansson |url=http://www.interviewmagazine.com/music/scarlett-johansson/2 |work=[[Interview_Magazine|Interview Magazine]] |date=2008-11-30 |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090520054511/http://www.interviewmagazine.com/music/scarlett-johansson/2 |archivedate=2009-05-20 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，谈及汤姆·威茨时她曾说道：“他的曲调太美了，声线也无比别致，我会用自己的方式处理汤姆·威茨的歌曲。<ref>{{cite web |first=Josh |last=Jackson |title=Scarlett Johansson and David Sitek talk Tom Waits Album |work=Paste Magazine |date=2008-02-13 |accessdate=2014-07-08 |url=http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2008/02/scarlett-johansson-and-david-sitek-talk-tom-waits.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210203631/http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2008/02/scarlett-johansson-and-david-sitek-talk-tom-waits.html |archive-date=2009-02-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>”2008年12月，报道称约翰逊计划继续出一张专辑，这张将全都是原创歌曲，她说：“我不想再做翻唱了，我会全心全意做这个原创项目，这是为未来考虑。<ref>{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson Says She'll Record Another Album, Still Has Leonard Cohen on the Brain|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1601310/scarlett-johansson-says-shell-record-another-album-still-has-leonard-cohen-on-the-brain/|publisher=MTV|date=2008-11-15|accessdate=2014-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715124453/http://www.mtv.com/news/1601310/scarlett-johansson-says-shell-record-another-album-still-has-leonard-cohen-on-the-brain/|archive-date=2014-07-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>”

2009年，约翰逊翻唱了[[杰夫·巴克利|杰夫·巴克利]]的歌曲《{{link-en|最后的道别|Last Goodbye (Jeff Buckley song)}}》，歌曲加入了《[[他其實沒那麼喜歡妳|他其實沒那麼喜歡妳]]》的原声大碟<ref>{{cite web |title=Scarlett Johansson Covers Jeff Buckley |publisher=Stereogum |date=2009-01-27 |accessdate=2014-07-08 |url=http://www.stereogum.com/48421/scarlett_johansson_covers_jeff_buckley/mp3s/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113005828/http://www.stereogum.com/48421/scarlett_johansson_covers_jeff_buckley/mp3s/ |archivedate=2014-11-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2009年9月8日，专辑《{{lang|en|{{link-en|Break Up|Break Up (album)}}}}》发行，这是一张由约翰逊和创作型歌手[[皮特·约恩|皮特·约恩]]合作完成的专辑，灵感源于[[碧姬·芭铎|碧姬·芭铎]]和[[塞吉·金斯伯格|塞吉·金斯伯格]]的二重唱<ref>{{cite news|first=Edna|last=Gundersen|title=Listen as Yorn, Johansson 'Break Up'|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/music/news/2009-05-21-break-up-album_N.htm|work=USA Today|date=2009-05-12|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804180239/http://www.usatoday.com/life/music/news/2009-05-21-break-up-album_N.htm|archive-date=2009-08-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。独立乐队{{Link-en|Steel Train|Steel Train}}发布专辑《{{lang|en|Terrible Thrills Vol. 1}}》，包含他们最爱的女歌手翻唱他们乐队的歌曲。约翰逊翻唱的《子弹》（{{lang|en|''Bullet''}}）是专辑的第一首曲目<ref>{{cite news|author=David|title=斯嘉丽-约翰逊翻唱Steel Train乐队歌曲|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/2010-07-23/11363027085.shtml|accessdate=2014-06-30|newspaper=新浪娱乐|date=2010-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714132840/http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/2010-07-23/11363027085.shtml|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.americansongwriter.com/2010/06/scarlett-johansson-tegan-and-sara-stump-for-steel-train|title=Scarlett Johansson, Tegan And Sara Stump For Steel Train|publisher=American Songwriter|date=2010-06-04|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110707133204/http://www.americansongwriter.com/2010/06/scarlett-johansson-tegan-and-sara-stump-for-steel-train/|archive-date=2011-07-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，约翰逊为纪录片《{{link-en|可怜虫和胡言乱语者|Wretches & Jabberers}}》献唱了一首原声，《整个一小时》（{{lang|en|''One Whole Hour''}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://finance.yahoo.com/news/J-Ralph-Assembles-iw-1696403363.html?x=0|title=J. Ralph Assembles Unbelievable Cast of Legendary Voices for 'Wretches & Jabberers' Out April 5, 2011|publisher=Finance.yahoo.com|date=2011-02-10|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004719/http://finance.yahoo.com/news/J-Ralph-Assembles-iw-1696403363.html?x=0|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/wretches-jabberers-soundtrack/id413744014|title="Wretches & Jabberers Soundtrack", by J. Ralph Featuring Various Artists, iTunes web site|publisher=Itunes.apple.com|date=2011-01-11|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004505/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/wretches-jabberers-soundtrack/id413744014|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年，约翰逊为纪录片《{{link-en|逐冰之旅|Chasing Ice}}》录制原声《{{lang|en|Before My Time}}》，这首歌曲也获得了2013年奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲提名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57563553/hear-5-oscar-nominees-for-best-original-song|title=Hear 5 Oscar nominees for Best Original Song|publisher=CBS News|date=2013-01-12|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130327003441/http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-207_162-57563553/hear-5-oscar-nominees-for-best-original-song/|archive-date=2013-03-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==广告赞助==
约翰逊曾出演[[卡尔文·克雷恩|卡尔文·克雷恩]]、[[欧莱雅|欧莱雅]]和[[路易·威登|路易·威登]]等品牌的广告<ref name="D&G" />，2009年起她还是西班牙{{link-en|芒果服饰|Mango (clothing)}}的代言人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sassybella.com/2009/05/news-bite-scarlett-mango-henry-holland-alex-wang-qa-angels-pregnant/ |title=News Bite: Scarlett for Mango, Henry Holland & Alex Wang Q&A, and are all the VS Angels pregnant? |publisher=Sassybella.com |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906005025/http://www.sassybella.com/2009/05/news-bite-scarlett-mango-henry-holland-alex-wang-qa-angels-pregnant/ |archive-date=2014-09-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年初，她与两位意大利设计师现身[[大都会艺术博物馆|大都会艺术博物馆]]服饰研究馆，随后宣布成为[[杜嘉班纳|杜嘉班纳]]新的化妆品分支的代言人<ref name="D&G">{{cite news|title=Scarlett likes it hot: Johansson goes for the Marilyn Monroe look in striking D&G ad|work=Daily Mail|location=UK|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1121883/Scarlett-likes-hot-Johansson-goes-Marilyn-Monroe-look-striking-D-G-ad.html|date=2009-01-19|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004922/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1121883/Scarlett-likes-hot-Johansson-goes-Marilyn-Monroe-look-striking-D-G-ad.html|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2009年7月31日，她以个人身份出现在伦敦的[[塞尔福里奇|塞尔福里奇]]百货商店，宣传推广杜嘉班纳的新化妆品产品<ref name="dolce">{{cite web|title=Scarlett Johansson Launches Dolce & Gabbana The Makeup in London|publisher=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|date=2009-07-29|accessdate=2014-07-08|url=http://stylenews.peoplestylewatch.com/2009/07/31/scarlett-johansson-launches-dolce-gabbana-the-makeup-in-london/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090802095412/http://stylenews.peoplestylewatch.com/2009/07/31/scarlett-johansson-launches-dolce-gabbana-the-makeup-in-london/|archive-date=2009-08-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，约翰逊签约为[[酩悦香槟|酩悦香槟]]的代言人，并多次出现在品牌广告和商业活动中，由此成为第一个担任香槟酒庄大使的好莱坞明星<ref name="Scarlett Johansson for Moët & Chandon">{{cite news|title=Scarlett Johannson for MOËT & CHANDON|work=Senatus|url=http://senatus.net/article/scarlett-johannson-for-moet-chandon|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140623141750/http://senatus.net/article/scarlett-johannson-for-moet-chandon/|archive-date=2014-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年1月，{{link-en|苏打气体|SodaStream}}汽水公司宣布约翰逊成为品牌首位全球大使<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.haaretz.com/business/1.568108 | title = Israeli firm SodaStream hires Scarlett Johansson as its new face | work = [[Haaretz|Haaretz]] | date = 2014-01-12 | accessdate = 2014-07-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140112194611/http://www.haaretz.com/business/1.568108 | archive-date = 2014-01-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=林杉, 路西|title=好莱坞女星代言饮料引争议 辞任慈善大使|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/ukchina/simp/entertainment/2014/01/140131_ent_scarlett_oxfam.shtml|accessdate=2014-07-01|newspaper=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2014-01-31}}</ref>。

==性感象征==
<!-- 注释出：[[File:Knightley_-_Johansson_-_Vanity_Fair_Full_Cover.jpg|right]] (右) 与[[湯姆·福特|湯姆·福特]]在《[[浮華世界_(杂志)|浮華世界]]》杂志好莱坞版2006年三月期上裸体出镜。]] -->
2006年3月，斯嘉丽·约翰逊、[[凯拉·奈特莉|凯拉·奈特莉]]和设计师[[汤姆·福特|汤姆·福特]]出现在《[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]]》杂志的封面，两位女士更是全裸出镜<ref>{{cite web|title=Table of Contents, March 2006|work=Vanity Fair|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/magazine/toc/contents-200603|accessdate=2010-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101128025813/http://www.vanityfair.com/magazine/toc/contents-200603|archive-date=2010-11-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Keith Wagstaff|title=Scarlett Johansson and Keira Knightley, Vanity Fair|url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2107768_2107767_2107763,00.html|accessdate=2014-07-01|date=2012-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630231838/http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2107768_2107767_2107763,00.html|archive-date=2014-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[美信|美信]]》杂志每年发布当年“最火辣100人”，2006年约翰逊位列第6<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.maxim.com/women/hot-100/article/2006-hot-100 |title=2006 Hot 100 Photos |work=[[Maxim_(magazine)|Maxim]] |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716234223/http://www.maxim.com/women/hot-100/article/2006-hot-100 |archivedate=2015-07-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，2007年位列第3<ref>{{cite web |title=2007 Top 100 Photos |url=http://www.maxim.com/girls/hot-100/76385/2007-hot-100.html?p=98 |publisher=Maxim |accessdate=2014-07-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090512135629/http://www.maxim.com/girls/hot-100/76385/2007-hot-100.html?p=98 |archivedate=2009-05-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，2008年位列第2<ref>{{cite web|title=2008 Hot 100|url=http://www.maxim.com/hot-100/2008-hot-100|publisher=Maxim|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705032947/http://www.maxim.com/hot-100/2008-hot-100|archive-date=2014-07-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2009年位列34<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maxim.com/hot-100/2009-hot-100#67|title=2009 Hot 100|work=[[Maxim_(magazine)|Maxim]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709212353/http://www.maxim.com/hot-100/2009-hot-100#67|archive-date=2014-07-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2010年位列14<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.maxim.com/hot100details/2010 |title=2010 HOT 100 LIST |work=[[Maxim_(magazine)|Maxim]] |accessdate=2015-07-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150424162143/http://www.maxim.com/hot100details/2010 |archivedate=2015-04-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，2011年位列14<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maxim.com/girls/2011-hot-100|title=2011 Hot 100|work=[[Maxim_(magazine)|Maxim]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705032800/http://www.maxim.com/girls/2011-hot-100|archive-date=2014-07-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2012年位列17<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.maxim.com/hot100details/2011 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150501033448/http://www.maxim.com/hot100details/2011 |archivedate=2015-05-01 |title=2012 Maxim Hot 100 |work=[[Maxim_(magazine)|Maxim]] |accessdate=2014-07-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，2013年位列15<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maxim.com/hot100/2013|title=Maxim 2013 Hot 100|work=[[Maxim_(magazine)|Maxim]]|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140708083449/http://www.maxim.com/hot100/2013|archive-date=2014-07-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年11月，约翰逊被《[[时尚先生_(刊物)|时尚先生]]》评为“当今最性感女性”<ref>{{cite news|title=Esquire: Scarlett Johansson 'Sexiest'|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/09/29/AR2006092900856.html|date=2006-09-29|accessdate=2006-09-29|work=The Washington Post|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130721050225/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/09/29/AR2006092900856.html|archive-date=2013-07-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2007年2月，《[[花花公子|花花公子]]》杂志将其列为当年“最性感名人”<ref name="BTPB07">{{cite news|url=http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/film-tv/news/iron-man-2-scarlett-johansson-fever-strikes-again-14782051.html|title=Iron Man 2: Scarlett Johansson fever strikes again.|date=2010-04-27|publisher=The Belfast Telegraph|accessdate=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100430044558/http://www.belfasttelegraph.co.uk/entertainment/film-tv/news/iron-man-2-scarlett-johansson-fever-strikes-again-14782051.html|archive-date=2010-04-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。自2005年起，《[[男人装|男人装]]》杂志更是经常把他列入百位性感女性之中<ref>{{cite news |title=Scarlett Johansson – Fulsome fantasy |url=http://www.fhm.com/girls/covergirls/scarlett-johansson |accessdate=2012-05-04 |work=《男人装》杂志 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120511221059/http://www.fhm.com/girls/covergirls/scarlett-johansson |archivedate=2012-05-11 }}</ref>。在《[[赛末点|赛末点]]》的拍摄过程中，伍迪·艾伦评价她“性感逼人”，而他本人则“很难在一个性感逼人、年轻貌美的女士面前显得格外风趣，因为这位女士比你还更谈吐幽默。<ref>{{cite news |title=Allen Overwhelmed by Johansson's Sexuality |publisher=Hollywood.com |accessdate=2014-07-08 |date=2006-06-27 |url=http://www.hollywood.com/news/Allen_Overwhelmed_by_Johanssons_Sexuality/3521442 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130104035831/http://www.hollywood.com/news/Allen_Overwhelmed_by_Johanssons_Sexuality/3521442 |archivedate=2013-01-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>”2010年，《[[GQ|GQ]]》杂志将其评为“年度宝贝”<ref>{{cite web|title=GQ's Babe of the Year Is Scarlett Johansson|url=http://iknowjack.radio.com/2010/11/16/gqs-babe-of-the-year-is-scarlett-johansson/|access-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101126170308/http://iknowjack.radio.com/2010/11/16/gqs-babe-of-the-year-is-scarlett-johansson/|archive-date=2010-11-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，《[[男性健康_(杂志)|男性健康]]》杂志将她评选为“百位史上最惹火女性”第12位<ref>{{cite web|title=The 100 Hottest Women of All-Time|url=http://www.menshealth.com/sex-women/hottest-women-all-time|work=Men's Health|accessdate=2014-07-01|year=2011|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69zudLdqP?url=http://www.menshealth.com/sex-women/hottest-women-all-time|archive-date=2012-08-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 个人生活 ==
约翰逊本人既庆祝[[犹太教|犹太教]]的[[光明节|光明节]]，也参加基督教的圣诞节<ref>{{cite news|title=Marvel Avengers Assemble – Scarlett Johansson interview|publisher=IndieLondon.co.uk|first=Rob|last=Carnevale|url=http://www.indielondon.co.uk/Film-Review/marvel-avengers-assemble-scarlett-johansson-interview|date=2012-05-06|access-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140605195737/http://www.indielondon.co.uk/Film-Review/marvel-avengers-assemble-scarlett-johansson-interview|archive-date=2014-06-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但她自称是犹太教徒<ref name="tirti">{{cite news|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/theticket/2012/0427/1224315215457.html|newspaper=The Irish Times|date=2012-04-27|title='I'm not anything like her...'|accessdate=2014-07-08|archivedate=2012-04-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427065747/http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/theticket/2012/0427/1224315215457.html|deadurl=yes|quote=Born in New York to a Danish architect father and a Jewish film producer mom, Johansson was exposed to cinema early and often.}}</ref><ref>[http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2007-08-21-scarlett-johansson-cover_N.htm "Hollywood enters the era of Scarlett Johansson"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2007-08-21-scarlett-johansson-cover_N.htm |date=20111214114822 }}, ''[[USA_Today|USA Today]]''</ref><ref>[http://www.femail.com.au/scarlett-johansson-the-spirit-interview.htm "Scarlett Johansson The Spirit Interview"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.femail.com.au/scarlett-johansson-the-spirit-interview.htm |date=20120209033900 }}, Femail.com</ref>。

人们常用“{{lang|en|ScarJo}}”这个昵称称呼她，但她很不喜欢，认为这个名字“恶心糟糕”<ref>Barker, Olivia. [http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/story/2011-12-15/Scarlett-Johansson/51976530/1 "Scarlett Johansson escapes the tabloid-gossip zoo"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/story/2011-12-15/Scarlett-Johansson/51976530/1 |date=20120214044803 }}. ''USA Today''. 2011-12-15</ref><ref>[http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-3445_162-57563692/q-a-scarlett-johansson "Q&A: Scarlett Johansson"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-3445_162-57563692/q-a-scarlett-johansson |date=20130929043332 }}. ''CBS News''. 2013-01-13</ref>。2014年5月，她在一份杂志中称：“我会把{{lang|en|ScarJo}}这个昵称跟流行歌手什么联系起来，听着很俗，而且显得慵懒轻浮。<ref>{{cite web|last=Spero|first=Jesse|title=Scarlett Johansson Slams Own Nickname|url=https://celebrity.yahoo.com/news/scarlett-johansson-slams-own-nickname-161439029.html|publisher=Yahoo!|date=2014-04-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413131814/https://celebrity.yahoo.com/news/scarlett-johansson-slams-own-nickname-161439029.html|archivedate=2014-04-13|accessdate=2014-07-05}}</ref>”

2011年9月14日，[[联邦调查局|FBI]]宣布其正在调查一桩针对约翰逊手机的网络入侵案件，这起入侵导致了约翰逊裸照外泄<ref>{{cite news|last=Winter|first=Jana|url=http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2011/09/14/nude-scarlett-johansson-shots-show-up-on-web-spur-call-to-fbi-report-says|title=FBI Investigating Alleged Nude Scarlett Johansson Photo Hack|publisher=Fox News|date=2011-09-14|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110923145025/http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2011/09/14/nude-scarlett-johansson-shots-show-up-on-web-spur-call-to-fbi-report-says/|archive-date=2011-09-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=龙龙|title=斯嘉丽-约翰逊裸照网上泄露 FBI介入调查|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/s/u/2011-09-15/09493416695.shtml|accessdate=2014-07-01|newspaper=新浪娱乐|date=2011-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714203914/http://ent.sina.com.cn/s/u/2011-09-15/09493416695.shtml|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，约翰逊宣称，这些照片是事发三年前，她自拍后传给当时的丈夫[[萊恩·雷諾斯|萊恩·雷諾斯]]的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/online/daily/2011/11/scarlett-johansson-december-cover-nude-pictures-sean-penn|title=Scarlett Johansson on Those Nude Photos She Sent to Ryan Reynolds: "I Know My Best Angles"|work=Vanity Fair|publisher=Condé Nast Publications|date=2011-11-01|accessdate=2011-11-24|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69goFadtk?url=http://www.vanityfair.com/online/daily/2011/11/scarlett-johansson-december-cover-nude-pictures-sean-penn|archive-date=2012-08-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=斯嘉丽 约翰逊证实裸照真实 曾发前夫瑞恩 雷诺兹|url=http://news.cntv.cn/20111102/113586.shtml|accessdate=2014-07-01|newspaper=国际在线娱乐|date=2011-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714185807/http://news.cntv.cn/20111102/113586.shtml|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。经过调查，居住于[[弗罗里达州|弗罗里达州]][[杰克逊维尔_(佛罗里达州)|杰克逊维尔]]的克里斯多夫·钱尼（{{lang|en|Christopher Chaney}}）涉嫌网络入侵，他本人对此供认不讳，并因而面临监禁，同时检察官要求其赔付约翰逊66000美元<ref>{{cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2012/06/scarlett-johansson-hacker-should-get-71-months-and-pay-celebs-money.html|work=Los Angeles Times|title=L.A. Now|accessdate=2014-03-29|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69goGRX8r?url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2012/06/scarlett-johansson-hacker-should-get-71-months-and-pay-celebs-money.html|archive-date=2012-08-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 恋爱婚姻 ===
2007年起，斯嘉丽·约翰逊开始与加拿大男星[[萊恩·雷諾斯|萊恩·雷諾斯]]约会<ref name="rreynold">{{cite news|last=Messer|first=Lesley|title=Scarlett Johansson & Ryan Reynolds Step Out in NYC|work=People|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20034177,00.html|date=2007-04-07|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070918185412/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20034177,00.html|archive-date=2007-09-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2008年5月，两人被爆订婚<ref>{{cite news|first=Alexis|last=Chiu|title=Scarlett Johansson & Ryan Reynolds Engaged!|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20197908,00.html|work=People|date=2008-05-05|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081030031540/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20197908,00.html|archive-date=2008-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年9月27日，这对情侣在加拿大[[托菲诺|托菲诺]]举行了一场低调的婚礼<ref name="rreynold"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20238093,00.html|title=Just Married!  — Secret Weddings, Ryan Reynolds, Scarlett Johansson|last=Hamm|first=Liza|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|date=2008-10-13|quote=The weekend-long bash took place at the rugged-yet-luxurious Clayoquot Wilderness Resort, a remote outpost near the Canadian seaside village of Tofino, B.C. Located on Vancouver Island|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004625/http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20238093,00.html|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=斯嘉丽-约翰逊：就要如此傲慢地调情|url=http://yule.sohu.com/20130925/n387198662.shtml|accessdate=2014-07-01|newspaper=壹读|date=2013-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714153228/http://yule.sohu.com/20130925/n387198662.shtml|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>，随后在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]购置价值280万美元的居所<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/healthylifestyle/news/scarlett-johansson-ryan-reynolds-buy-28-million-home-2010128|title=Scarlett Johansson, Ryan Reynolds Buy $2.8 Million Home|work=Us Magazine|access-date=2012-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100819135631/http://www.usmagazine.com/healthylifestyle/news/scarlett-johansson-ryan-reynolds-buy-28-million-home-2010128|archive-date=2010-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但是好景不常，2010年12月14日，两人宣布和平分手，此前已分居半年<ref>{{cite news|title=斯嘉丽-约翰逊宣布离婚 与瑞安-雷诺兹和平分手|url=http://ent.ifeng.com/idolnews/eurousa/detail_2010_12/16/3538247_0.shtml|accessdate=2014-07-01|newspaper=[[新京报|新京报]]|date=2010-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714114641/http://ent.ifeng.com/idolnews/eurousa/detail_2010_12/16/3538247_0.shtml|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年7月，二人正式离婚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebritynews/news/ryan-reynolds-scarlett-johanssons-divorce-finalized-201117|title=Ryan Reynolds, Scarlett Johansson's Divorce Finalized|work=Us Weekly|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110916193216/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebritynews/news/ryan-reynolds-scarlett-johanssons-divorce-finalized-201117|archive-date=2011-09-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=比尼|title=斯嘉丽·约翰逊想念前夫 被指渴望与其破镜重圆|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20111207/000225.htm|accessdate=2014-07-01|newspaper=腾讯娱乐|date=2011-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714220336/http://ent.qq.com/a/20111207/000225.htm|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年11月，约翰逊开始与广告公司总监、法国人罗曼·达瑞克（{{lang|en|Romain Dauriac}}）约会<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/pictures-scarlett-johansson-kisses-french-boyfriend-romain-dauriac-2012712|title=PICTURES: Scarlett Johansson Kisses French Boyfriend Romain Dauriac|work=US Weekly|date=2012-12-07|last=Eggenberger|first=Nicole|access-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140605171221/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/pictures-scarlett-johansson-kisses-french-boyfriend-romain-dauriac-2012712|archive-date=2014-06-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2013年11月，两人宣布订婚<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/09/05/showbiz/scarlett-johansson-engaged/?hpt=hp_t2|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2013-09-05|title=Actress Scarlett Johansson is engaged|access-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170911221635/http://www.cnn.com/2013/09/05/showbiz/scarlett-johansson-engaged/?hpt=hp_t2|archive-date=2017-09-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2014年9月5日，她的發言人證實喬韓森已產下一女，<ref>{{cite news|author=田颖|title=“女神”斯嘉丽·约翰逊当妈妈了|url=http://epaper.bjnews.com.cn/html/2014-09/06/content_533741.htm?div=-1|accessdate=2014-09-06|newspaper=[[新京报|新京报]]|date=2014-09-06|archive-date=2021-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211002031945/http://epaper.bjnews.com.cn/html/2014-09/06/content_533741.htm?div=-1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=姜一平|title=斯嘉丽·约翰逊喜得一女 性感女神晋升辣妈|url=http://ent.china.com.cn/2014-09/05/content_33438725.htm|accessdate=2014-09-05|newspaper=中国网|date=2014-09-05|archive-date=2019-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508005521/http://ent.china.com.cn/2014-09/05/content_33438725.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年9月，與羅曼·達瑞克正式離婚<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/2017/09/13/scarlett-johansson-single-again-divorce-finalized/663656001/ |title=Scarlett Johansson is single again as divorce is finalized |date=2017-09-13 |work=USA Today |access-date=2017-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914161539/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/2017/09/13/scarlett-johansson-single-again-divorce-finalized/663656001/ |archive-date=2017-09-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年5月，消息指约翰逊与《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》首席联合编剧[[科林·约斯特|科林·约斯特]]交往<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/scarlett-johansson-colin-jost-red-carpet-photos_us_5a21787be4b0a02abe90d1ee |title=Introducing ScarJost: Scarlett Johansson And Colin Jost Go Public |last=Sieczkowski |first=Cavan |date=2017-12-01 |work=The Huffington Post |access-date=2018-05-20 |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517210100/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/scarlett-johansson-colin-jost-red-carpet-photos_us_5a21787be4b0a02abe90d1ee |archive-date=2018-05-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，两人于2019年5月订婚<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.people.com/movies/scarlett-johansson-colin-jost-engaged/ |title=Scarlett Johansson and SNL's Colin Jost Are Engaged After Two Years of Dating |work=People |first=Karen |last=Mizoguchil |date=May 19, 2019 |access-date=May 20, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520081855/https://people.com/movies/scarlett-johansson-colin-jost-engaged/ |archive-date=2019-05-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最终于2020年10月确认结婚<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/scarlett-johansson-colin-jost-marry-private-ceremony-snl-black-widow-b1432035.html|title=Scarlett Johansson and Colin Jost wed in private ceremony|date=2020-10-29|work=The Independent|access-date=2020-10-29|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031201501/https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/love-sex/scarlett-johansson-colin-jost-wedding-married-ceremony-snl-black-widow-b1432246.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，两人的儿子于2021年8月出生。<ref>{{cite news|last=VanHoose|first=Benjamin|last2=Leonard|first2=Elizabeth|url=https://people.com/parents/scarlett-johansson-colin-jost-welcome-first-baby-together/|title=Scarlett Johansson and Husband Colin Jost Welcome First Baby Together|work=People|date=2021-08-18|access-date=2021-08-18|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210818211717/https://people.com/parents/scarlett-johansson-colin-jost-welcome-first-baby-together/|archive-date=2021-08-18}}</ref>

==社会行动==

===慈善工作===
2005年，约翰逊成为[[乐施会|乐施会]]的全球大使<ref name="Oxfam">{{cite news |url=http://www.oxfam.org/en/news/ambassadors/scarlett_johansson |title=Scarlett Johansson, Oxfam Ambassador |archivedate=2007-10-12 |publisher=Oxfam International |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012115042/http://oxfam.org/en/news/ambassadors/scarlett_johansson |accessdate=2008-02-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2008年3月，在一场{{lang|en|[[eBay|eBay]]}}慈善拍卖中，一位英国的买主以20000英镑拍得了与约翰逊的20分钟约会，他将与约翰逊携手出席《[[他其實沒那麼喜歡妳|他其實沒那麼喜歡妳]]》的全球首映<ref>{{cite news|title=斯嘉丽做慈善 拍卖“约会”与其携手出席首映|url=http://ent.163.com/08/0304/11/466IUT1700032DGD.html|accessdate=2014-07-01|newspaper=新华社|date=2008-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402153809/http://ent.163.com/08/0304/11/466IUT1700032DGD.html|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，而这笔款项也将交给乐施会<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7295871.stm |title=Fan pays £20,000 to date Scarlett |date=2008-03-14 |accessdate=2014-07-08 |work=BBC News |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090103011945/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7295871.stm |archive-date=2009-01-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年1月，约翰逊辞去了乐施会的慈善大使职务<ref>{{cite news|author=尹倩雯|title=斯嘉丽·约翰逊首度登杂志回应饮品广告争议|url=http://fashion.huanqiu.com/news/2014-02/4862134.html|accessdate=2014-07-01|newspaper=环球网|date=2014-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714193011/http://fashion.huanqiu.com/news/2014-02/4862134.html|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1200393/scarlett-johansson-criticised-over-sodastream|title=Scarlett Johansson Criticised Over SodaStream|date=2014-01-24|publisher=Sky.com|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140204041033/http://news.sky.com/story/1200393/scarlett-johansson-criticised-over-sodastream|archive-date=2014-02-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>，起因是她代言以色列汽水公司苏打气体（{{lang|en|SodaStream}}），而该公司在[[约旦河西岸|约旦河西岸]]的犹太人屯垦区开设了工厂，乐施会声明反对与剥削屯垦区的犹太企业做生意，认为这侵犯了[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]人的利益<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thelede.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/01/23/scarlett-johanssons-sodastream-endorsement-deal-conflicts-with-charity-work-aid-group-says|title=Scarlett Johansson’s SodaStream Endorsement Deal Conflicts With Charity Work, Aid Group Says|date=2014-01-23|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125232511/http://thelede.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/01/23/scarlett-johanssons-sodastream-endorsement-deal-conflicts-with-charity-work-aid-group-says/|archive-date=2014-01-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。约翰逊回应称，她和乐施会“在[[抵制、撤资和制裁|抵制、撤资和制裁]]的反以色列运动上，有着根本性的观点差异”<ref name=bbc20140130>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-25958176 |title=Scarlett Johansson quits Oxfam role over SodaStream row |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2014-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309102041/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-25958176 |archive-date=2014-03-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，她辩护说，这家公司致力于“为以色列和巴勒斯坦的和平牵线搭桥”<ref>{{cite web|author=Jason Gay|title=走进斯嘉丽·约翰逊的世界|url=http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20140415/lux122749.asp|publisher=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|accessdate=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714133436/http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20140415/lux122749.asp|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。乐施会接受了她的辞职并声称：“我们非常感激她的诸多贡献……她一直帮助我们宣传自然灾害的破坏，并为拯救生命和抗击贫困而筹款。<ref name=oxfam>{{cite press release |url=http://www.oxfam.org/en/pressroom/reactions/oxfam-accepts-resignation-scarlett-johansson |title=Oxfam accepts resignation of Scarlett Johansson |publisher=Oxfam International |date=2014-01-30 |access-date=2014-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140717114053/http://www.oxfam.org/en/pressroom/reactions/oxfam-accepts-resignation-scarlett-johansson |archive-date=2014-07-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>O'Neil, Brendan. [http://blogs.telegraph.co.uk/news/brendanoneill2/100257423/three-cheers-for-scarlett-johanssons-stand-against-the-ugly-illiberal-boycott-israel-movement/ "Three cheers for Scarlett Johansson's stand against the ugly, illiberal Boycott Israel movement"] {{Wayback|url=http://blogs.telegraph.co.uk/news/brendanoneill2/100257423/three-cheers-for-scarlett-johanssons-stand-against-the-ugly-illiberal-boycott-israel-movement/ |date=20140303230945 }}, ''The Telegraph'', 2014-01-30 [2015-03-26]</ref>”

===政治态度===
作为美国公民，约翰逊注册为{{link-en|独立选民|Independent (voter)}}<ref name="T-IND">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/1577733/Scarlett-Johansson-supports-Barack-Obama.html|title=Scarlett Johansson supports Barack Obama|last=Elsworth|first=Catherine|date=2008-02-05|work=The Daily Telegraph|location=UK|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090507231600/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/1577733/Scarlett-Johansson-supports-Barack-Obama.html|archive-date=2009-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[2004年美国总统选举|2004年美国总统选举]]中，她支持[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]选人[[约翰·克里|约翰·克里]]。当年的结果是[[小布什|小布什]]获得连任，她说：“（我很）失望。我觉得相当多的美国人都会失望。<ref name="cmusic2">{{cite news|title=Johansson: Americans disappointed by Bush's re-election|publisher=ContactMusic|url=http://www.contactmusic.com/news-article/johansson-americans-disappointed-by-bushs-re-election|date=2005-08-23|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004749/http://www.contactmusic.com/news-article/johansson-americans-disappointed-by-bushs-re-election|archive-date=2014-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>”

约翰逊也曾为[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]拉票<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2008-01-30-celebrity-politics_N.htm|title=Primary time for celebs: Star power floods political arena|work=USA Today|date=2008-01-30|accessdate=2014-07-08|first=Gary|last=Strauss|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604034918/http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2008-01-30-celebrity-politics_N.htm|archive-date=2011-06-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>：2008年1月，她现身[[爱荷华州|爱荷华州]]，参与竞选活动<ref name="DTKJ">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2008/01/15/politics/uwire/main3718699.shtml|title=Impact of Student Voters Questioned|last=Johnson|first=Katelyn|date=2008-01-15|publisher={{link-en|Daily Trojan|Daily Trojan}}|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101121194245/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2008/01/15/politics/uwire/main3718699.shtml|archive-date=2010-11-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>；此外还出现在{{le|康奈爾學院|Cornell College}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Actress Scarlett Johansson appears |url=http://webapps.cornellcollege.edu/events/2008/01/02/1319/ |publisher=Cornell College |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717222140/http://webapps.cornellcollege.edu/events/2008/01/02/1319/ |archivedate=2015-07-17 |accessdate=2014-07-08 |date=2008-01-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>和[[卡尔顿学院|卡尔顿学院]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Actress Scarlett Johansson Appears at Carleton for Obama|url=https://apps.carleton.edu/news/features/?story_id=378757|accessdate=2014-07-01|newspaper=Carleton News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714183955/https://apps.carleton.edu/news/features/?story_id=378757|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>；2008年，约翰逊还参与[[黑眼豆豆|黑眼豆豆]]主唱{{lang|en|[[Will.i.am|Will.i.am]]}}的歌曲《是的，我们能做到》（{{lang|en|''Yes, We Can''}}）的MV，歌曲灵感便来源于奥巴马的演讲<ref>{{cite news|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/idUKN0519585420080207|title=Musicians rock for Barack on Super Tuesday|agency=Reuters|date=2008-02-05|accessdate=2014-07-08|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920055135/https://uk.reuters.com/article/idUKN0519585420080207|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年2月7日，为支持奥巴马连任，约翰逊和美国时尚界人士[[安娜·温特|安娜·温特]]主持了一次筹款活动，并发布了一系列支持奥巴马的时尚用品，例如印有奥巴马名字和竞选口号的T恤、提包和坠饰<ref>[http://www.ibtimes.com/articles/295274/20120208/obama-runway-win-2012-fashion-line-features.htm "Obama 'Runway to Win' 2012 Photos: Fashion Line Features Marc Jacobs, Derek Lam"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/articles/295274/20120208/obama-runway-win-2012-fashion-line-features.htm |date=20120210094536 }} ''[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]'', 2012-02-08</ref>。在{{link-en|2012年民主党全国大会|2012 Democratic National Convention}}上，她向选民发表演说，呼吁支持奥巴马连任，也希望年轻选民多多参与<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0912/80868.html |title=Scarlett Johansson DNC speech (text, video) |agency=Politico |date=2012-09-06 |accessdate=2015-07-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140906004540/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0912/80868.html |archivedate=2014-09-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

